<chapter id="intro">
<title
>Ukwazisa</title>

<para
>I &kmail; Iqela liyakwamkela kwi &kmail; umsebenzisi-umposi ongumhlobo we Meko-bume ye K Desktop. Inqaku lethu kukwenza umposi omhle kwaye ongenantandabuzo ngaphandle kokunikezela ngamandla. </para>

<para
>Ukuba uke wacwangcisa umxhasi we email kwi &UNIX; ndlela phambi kokuba, siphakamise ukuba ufunda ngapha kwe <link linkend="getting-started"
>Ifumana uqalo</link
> icandelo kuqala ukuze ucwangciso lwakho luhambe mpuluswa.</para>

<para
>Ukusukela ukuba abantu abaninzi bengafundi xwebhu, nalu uqokelelo lweencam ezininzi eziluncedo:</para>

<itemizedlist
> <listitem
> <para
>Awunakusebenzisa imouse yakhop ukusebenzisa i &kmail;. Yonke into izakwenzeka ngezitshixo. &kmail; ixhasa zonke ezisezantsi izitshixo njenge <keycap
>Tab</keycap
> (switsha phakathi kweglasi). Eli qhinga li: <keycap
>Utolo lasekhohlo</keycap
>/<keycap
>Utolo lasekunene</keycap
> soloko uxhuma kumyalezo odlulileyo/olandelayo, kodwa xa ubamba phantsi i &Ctrl;, ungasebenzisa i <keycap
>Utolo lasekhohlo</keycap
>/<keycap
>Utolo lasekunene</keycap
> ukul;awula kwiglasi yencwadi ezineenkcukacha ne <keycap
>utolo oluphezulu</keycap
>/<keycap
>utolo olusezantsi</keycap
> ukulawula kwiglasi ye Headers. Sebenzisa i <keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>Isithuba</keycap
></keycombo
> ukukhetha incwadi eneenkcukacha oyilawuleyo.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> ungakhetha okubhaliweyo kwaye uyitsale jikelele nge mouse.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Noxa i &kmail; ingaqwalaselwa njengemeleyo ungagcina izimamva zemiyalezo yakho, &ie; khuphela nje iifayile kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> kwindawo ekhuselekileyo.</para
> </listitem
> </itemizedlist>

<para
>&kmail;'iphepha lasekhaya lise <ulink url="http://kmail.kde.org"
>http://kmail.kde.org</ulink
>, indawo yokugcina yoluhlu loposo lombhekisi phambili lukwi <ulink url="http://lists.kde.org/?l=kde-kmail&amp;r=1&amp;w=2"
>lists.kde.org</ulink
>.</para>

<para
>Nceda chaza i bugs kwi &kmail; usebenzisa i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Uncedo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Chaza i bug...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>.</para>

<para
>Sinethemba lokuba uyakuyithanda i &kmail;!</para>

</chapter>

<chapter id="getting-started">
<title
>Ifumana uqalo</title>

<para
>Olu kukwazisa okufutshane kwi &kmail; nosebenziso lwayo ukuze uqale ukusebenza ngayo. Oluninzi-olunzulu ulwazi bona i <link linkend="using-kmail"
>Usebenzisa i &kmail;</link
> icandelo. Qaphela ukuba i &kmail;'ufako lwayo luchazwa kwi <link linkend="installation"
>i appendix</link
>.</para>

<para
>Ibhenisa i &kmail; ngexesha lokuqala lenza ulawulo olubizwa ngokuba yi <filename class="directory"
>Iposi</filename
> iqulathe iifayile eziquphayo (<filename
>inbox</filename
>, <filename
>outbox</filename
>, <filename
>iposi-ethunyelweyo</filename
>, <filename
>umonakalo</filename
> ne <filename
>imizobo</filename
>) kulawulo lwakho lasekhaya. Sebenzisa i <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guimenuitem
> </menuchoice
> ukungenisa ulwazi oluquphileyo ngoko i &kmail; izakukwazi ukugcina ngendlela kwaye ithumele imiyalezo yakho.</para>

<para
>Iwindow yokuqwalasela iqulathe amacandelo asixhenxe: <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Umsebenzi womnatha</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Inkangeleko</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Mime Headers</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Ukhuseleko</guilabel
>, ne <guilabel
>Exubeneyo</guilabel
>. Ukuqala ukuthumela nokufumana imiyalezo uzakutshintsha kuphela izicwangciso kwi <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>Umsebenzi womnatha</guilabel
> tabs.</para>

<sect1 id="setting-your-identity">
<title
>Icwangcisa uqwalaselo lwakho</title>

<para
>Izicwangciso kwi <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> tab zijonge phambili kakuhle. Gcwalisa i <guilabel
>Igama</guilabel
> umhlaba nge gama elipheleleyo lakho (&eg; <userinput
>John Doe</userinput
>) ne <guilabel
>Iqela elinegunya</guilabel
> umhlaba (eyodwa) ngolwazi olululo. Elandelayo, gcwalisa i <guilabel
>Idilesi ye Email</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>Phendula-Kwidilesi</guilabel
> (eyodwa) umhlaba ngedilesi yakho ye email. Ukuba usebenzisa i<application
>PGP</application
> okanye <application
>GnuPG</application
> ufuna ukucwangcisa uqwalaselo kwi<guilabel
>PGP Uqwalaselo loMsebenzisi </guilabel
> umhlaba.</para>

<para
>Eyodwa, cwangcisa indawo yefayile yakho yotyikityo kwi <guilabel
>Ifayile yotyikityo</guilabel
> umhlaba. Ukuba ufuna utyikityo olujikelezayo, ungakhankanya udweliso lwenkqubo kwaye khangela i <guilabel
>Ifayile yibhokisiyodweliso</guilabel
> lwenkqubo.</para>

<para
>Ukuba udibanisa uqwalaselo olutsha, i <guilabel
>Dibanisa Isithuthi...</guilabel
> iqhosha lizakuvela (eli qhosha alisekho kwi <guilabel
>Engagqibekanga</guilabel
> uqwalaselo). Ikuvumela uqwalasele indlela yokuthumela imiyalezo woqwalaselo oluthile, &eg; ungafuna ukusebenzisa eyahlukileyo i <acronym
>SMTP</acronym
> umncedisi wenye yabaqwalaseli bakho.</para>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="setting-up-your-account">
<title
>Icweangcisa ityala lakho</title>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Umsebenzi womnatha</guilabel
> tab iqulathe izicwangciso ezixelela i &kmail; indlela yokuthumela nokwamkela eyakho i email. Ezininzi izicwangciso zingahluka ngokuxhomekeke kwisicwangciso sendlela yakho naku didi lomsebenzi womnatha umncedisi weposi wakho abekwe kulo. Ukuba awusazi isicwangciso omawusikhethe okanye omawukufake emhlabeni, dibana noMnikezi weNkonzo ye Internet yakho (<acronym
>ISP</acronym
>) okanye Umphathi wendlela.</para>

<sect2 id="sending-mail">
<title
>Ithumela iposi</title>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Ithumela Iposi</guilabel
> icandelo linikeza iinketho ezimbini zokuthumela imiyalezo: <guilabel
>sendmail</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>SMTP</guilabel
>. <application
>Sendmail</application
> inophindo olunzima ukulicwangcisa, ngoko ukuba awunayo kwaphela esebenzayo <application
>sendmail</application
> uqwalaselo, khetha <guilabel
>SMTP</guilabel
> kwaye gcwalisa i <guilabel
>Umncedisi</guilabel
> umhlaba ngegama nethambeka lomncedisi wakho weposi. awuzukufuna ukutshintsha i <guilabel
>Izibuko</guilabel
> isicwangciso (okungagqibekanga yi <userinput
>25</userinput
>).</para>

<para
>Ukuba ufuna ukusebenzisa i <application
>sendmail</application
> kwaye usebenzisa udibaniso locofo-phezulu, landela imiyalelo yokucwangcisa yodibaniso locofo-phezulu kwi <link linkend="faq"
>FAQ</link
> icandelo.</para>

<para
>Indlela yokuthumela imiyalezo eqwalaselwe apha izakusetyenziselwa uqwalselo olungagqibekanga lwakho kunye nazo zonke ezinye ingqwalasela ezingenandlela yazo yokuthumela imiyalezo. Ungasebenzisa iindlela ezahlukileyo zokuthumela imiyalezo zengqwalaselo ezhlukileyo ngokuzidibanisa nge <guilabel
>Dibanisa Isithuthi...</guilabel
> iqhosha kwi <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> icandelo.</para>

</sect2>
      
<sect2 id="properties">
<title
>Iimpahla</title>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Iimpahla</guilabel
> icandelo likuvumela uqwalasele njani nanini imiyalezo ithunyelwa.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Okungagqibekanga kuthumela indlela</guilabel
> ikuvumela uchaze ukuba kwenzeka ntoni xa umyalezo uthunyelwe. Ukuba <guilabel
>Thumela ngoku</guilabel
> i khethiwe, umyalezo uthunyelwa kumncedisi weposi ngokukhawuleza, ngexesha ukuba <guilabel
>Thumela mva</guilabel
> ikhethiwe, umyalezo uyafoliswa kwibhokisi yangaphandle mva nge <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Thumela Okufolisiweyo</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> umyalelo okanye ngokuzenzekelayo xa ukhangela iposi yakho, kuxhomekeke kwizicwangciso kwi <guilabel
>Exubeneyo</guilabel
> tab.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Impahla yoMyalezo</guilabel
> ikuvumela ukhethe indlela umyalezo wakho uzaku enkhowudwa ngayo xa uthunyelwa. <guilabel
>Vumela 8-amasuntswana</guilabel
> ithetha ukuba i &kmail; izakuthumela umyalezo wakho kwi 8 amasuntswana <acronym
>ASCII</acronym
>, ithetha ukuba bonke abasebenzi abathile abanjengeeleta ezonyuliweyo zizakuthunyelwa njengoko-zinjalo. Ukuba <guilabel
>MIME Compliant (Iphindwe Ishicilelwe)</guilabel
> ikhethiwe, abasebenzi abathile bazaku enkhowudwa usebenzisa esezantsi i &MIME; enkhowudingi, enokuhanjiswa ngaphezulu kwezinye iindlela zokuposa kune 8-amasuntswana <acronym
>ASCII</acronym
>. Uqhele ukungafuni ukutshintsha okungagqibekanga. </para>

<para
>Nge <guilabel
>Umyalelo wakuqala</guilabel
> ungakhankanya umyalelo ozakuphunyezwa phambi kokuba imiyalezo yakho ikhethwe.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Qinisekisa phambi kokuthumela</guilabel
> yenza incoko yababini ecela, lonke ixesha unqakraza <guilabel
>Thumela ngoku</guilabel
>, ukuba ngenene ufuna ukuthumela iposi yakho.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="receiving-mail">
<title
>Iposi engenayo</title>

<para
>Ukucwangcisa ityala ungamkela iposi, cinezela i <guibutton
>Dibanisa...</guibutton
> iqhosha kwi <guilabel
>Iposi Engenayo</guilabel
> icandelo. Uzakunceda ngodidi lwetyala. Abasebenzisi abaninzi banokukhetha <guilabel
>Pop3</guilabel
> okanye <guilabel
>IMAP</guilabel
>.</para>

<para
>Emva kokucinezela <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> uzakunikwa ngayo i <guilabel
>Dibanisa Ityala</guilabel
> window. Kuqala, gcwalisa i <guilabel
>Igama</guilabel
> umhla ukunika igama ityala lakho. Ungakhetha naliphi igama olithandayo. <guilabel
>Login</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Igama eligqithisiweyo</guilabel
>, ne <guilabel
>Inginginya</guilabel
> izakugcwaliswa ngolwazi olululo kweyakho <acronym
>ISP</acronym
> okanye Umphathi wendlela. Awufuni kutshintsha i <guilabel
>Izibuko</guilabel
> isicwangciso (okungagqibekanga kwe POP3 is <userinput
>110</userinput
>, okungagqibekanga kwe IMAP yi <userinput
>143</userinput
>).</para>

<sect3 id="receiving-mail-imap">
<title
>Iinketho ezayame kuphela kwi IMAP</title>

<para
>Ukuba usebenzisa i IMAP, ungakhankanya ngokukodwa umendo kwi <guilabel
>Isimaphambili kwincwadi ezineenkcukacha</guilabel
> umhlaba. Oku kuxelela &kmail; apho ingafumana khona iincwadi ezineenkcukacha kumncedisi. Ukuba kwakhona unetyala leqokobhe kumncedisi kwaye iiposi zigcinwa kulawulo lwakho lasekhaya inokubaluncedo ukugcina iiposi kulawulo olusezantsi <filename class="directory"
>/Mail/</filename
>. Sebenzisa oku njengexabiso kwi <guilabel
>Isimaphambili kwincwadi ezineenkcukacha</guilabel
> umhlaba ukuze i &kmail; ingazixubi iifayile zebhokisi yeposi nezinye iifayile. Ukuba awunamdla kulo msebenzi, shiya ngokulula umhlaba ungenanto.</para>

<para
>Ukuba ukhangela <guilabel
>cima ngokuzenzekelayo imiyalezo ecinyiweyo</guilabel
> &kmail; isusa iiposi ozicimileyo kuMncedisi nje ukuba ushiya incwadi eneenkcukacha. Kungenjalo iiposi ziphawulwe kuphela njengezicinyiweyo kwaye kuxhomekeke kuwe ukuphawula iincwadi ngokusebenzisa umba wemenu <guimenuitem
>Phawula zonke iincwadi ezineenkcukacha</guimenuitem
>.</para>

<para
>Ukuba ukhangela <guilabel
>Bonisa iincwadi ezifihlakeleyo</guilabel
>, iincwadi ezinamagama aqala ngechaphaza ayaboniswa nawo.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="receiving-mail-pop3">
<title
>Iinketho ezijolise kwi POP3</title>

<para
>Khetha <guilabel
>Cima iposi kumncedisi</guilabel
>ukuba awufuni ukushiya imiyalezo yakho kumncedisi emva kokuba uyilayishe ezantsi.</para>

<para
>Khetha <guilabel
>Khupha ngaphandle kwi &quot;Khangela Iposi&quot;</guilabel
> ukuba awufuni kukhangela ityala naphi na usebenzisa i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Khangela iposi</guimenu
></menuchoice
>. Ungakhangela kwakhona imiyalezo emitsha kweli tyala nge <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Khangela Iposi kwi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>.</para>

<para
>Khetha <guilabel
>Yenza ukhangelo lweposi lexeshana</guilabel
> ukuba ufuna i &kmail; ukukhangela imiyalezo emitsha ngokuzenzekelayo. Isithuba singakhankanywa ngezantsi phantsi kwe <guilabel
>Khangela isithuba (imizuzu)</guilabel
>.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>ibhokisi yangaphakathi</guilabel
> iyincwadi engagqibekanga yeposi engenayo. Ukuba ufuna ukutshintsha lo nto ngesizathu esithile, ungakwenza oko nge <guilabel
>Incwadi yendawo engongileyo</guilabel
>. Kodwa okufunayo yi <link linkend="filters"
>filter</link
>, engenanto yakwenza nolu khetho.</para>

<para
>Nge <guilabel
>Umyalelo wokuqala</guilabel
> ungakhankanya naluphi na udweliso lwenkqubo i &kmail; ezakuliphumeza nje phambi kokuthatha iposi. Nceda khankanya umendo opheleleyo kwaye qaphela ukuba i &kmail; ayizukuqhubeka lude lube udweliso lwenkqubo lubuyiselwe.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="receiving-mail-imap-pop3">
<title
>Iinketho zazo zombini i IMAP ne POP3</title>

<para
>Ukuba ukhetha <guilabel
>Gcina POP igama eligqithisiweyo kwifayile yoqwalaselo</guilabel
> resp. <guilabel
>Gcina IMAP igama eligqithisiweyo kwifayile yoqwalaselo</guilabel
> &kmail; izakukhumbula igama lakho eligqithisiweyo ukuze ungabinakuchwetheza yona lonke ixesha uqala i &kmail; kwaye thatha iposi entsha.</para>

<warning
><para
>Lumkiswa ukuba asinakufihla ngenene igama lakho oligqithisileyo, ngoko abantu abanokunikeza iifayile zakho zoqwalaselo (&eg; umphathi wendlela) angafumana lula igama lakho ukuba ukhetha olu khetho.</para
></warning>

<para
>&kmail; ixhasa ufihla igqitha kwi <guilabel
>SSL</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>TLS</guilabel
> (<guilabel
>TLS</guilabel
> zinokukhethwa ukuba ikhona)</para
> 

<para
>Ye POP3 &kmail; ixhasa <guilabel
>Cacisa okubhaliweyo</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>ENGENANTO</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>CRAM-MD5</guilabel
> and <guilabel
>APOP</guilabel
> ububhali. <guilabel
>APOP</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>CRAM-MD5</guilabel
> zikhuselekile ngokwazo, zonke ezinye iinketho zikhuseleke kuphela xa zisetyenziswa zonke nge <guilabel
>SSL</guilabel
> okanye <guilabel
>TLS</guilabel
>. Ungasebenzisakuphela i <guilabel
>Cacisa okubhaliweyo</guilabel
> ukuba umncedisi wakho akaxhasi nayiphi kwenye yendlela zobubhali. Ngokudibeneyo, ye IMAP <guilabel
>Engaziwayo</guilabel
> iyaxhaswa.</para>

<para
>Ngoku ulungile ukuthumela nokwamkela iposi! Ye IMAP, nqakraza kwi <guilabel
>+</guilabel
> phawula kumthi wencwadi eneenkcukacha kwi &kmail;eyoqobo i window. &kmail; ngoku idibanisa kumncedisi wakho kwaye ibonisa iincwadi ezineenkcukacha ezifumanayo. Ye POP3 sebenzisa <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Khangela Iposi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>.</para>

</sect3>

</sect2>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="testing-your-setup">
<title
>Ivavanya ucwangciso lwakho</title>

<para
>Kuqala, ungazithumelela ngokwakho umyalezo ukuvavanya olwakho uqwalaselo. Ukuthumela umyalezo, betha <keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>N</keycap
></keycombo
>, khetha i <guiicon
>Umyalezo Omtsha</guiicon
> icon (ikhasi elingenato lephepha) okanye khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Umyalezo Omtsha...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> umba wemenu. I <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window uzakuvela. Gcwalisa i <guilabel
>Kwi:</guilabel
> umhlaba ngedilesi yakho ye email kwaye chwetheza enye into kwi <guilabel
>Umxholo</guilabel
> umhlaba. Thumela umyaleso ngokukhetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Thumela ngoku</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>.</para>
      
<para
>Ukukhangela eyakho i email, khetha <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Khangela Iposi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Kwikona esezantsi ekunene kwe window engundoqo, ibar yenkqubela izakubonisa ukuba mingaphi imiyalezo elayishwe ezantsi. Ukuba wamkela umyalezo owuthumeleyo, ngoku siyavuyisana nawe! Ukuba, njengoko, usamkela nayiphi na imposiso yemiyalezo ngexesha uvavanya ucwangciso lwakho, qiniseka ukuba udibaniso lomsebenzi wakho womnatha uyasebenza kwaye khangela kwakhona izicwangciso zakho ngokukhetha <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Qwalasela &kmail;...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
></para>

</sect1>

</chapter>

<chapter id="using-kmail">
<title
>Usebenzisa i &kmail;</title>

<sect1 id="the-mail-reader-window">
<title
>Iwindow Engundoqo</title>

<para
>Iwindow engundoqo yiwindow evela xa i &kmail; iqaliwe. Yahlulwe ngokwamaqela amathathu:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ulwahlulo lwencwadi ezineenkcukacha (ulwahlulo lasekhohlo)</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Olu lwahlulo luqulathe uluhlu lwencwadi zomyalezo (olunye udweliso lweenkqubo ze email zibabiza ngokuba zibhokisi zeposi). Ukuba kukho inani emva kwegama lencwadi eneenkcukacha oku kwalatha ukuba le ncwadi iqulathe iiposi ezingafundwayo. Ukukhetha incwadi eneenkcukacha, nqakraza lula kuyo. Imiyalezo equlathiweyo kwincwadi izakuvela ngoku kulwahlulo lwe Headers. Inani lemiyalezo engafundwayo nenani elipheleleyo lemiyalezo kwincwadi ekhethiweyo ibonisiwe ngoku kwibar yendawo engatshintshiyo. Iincwadi zingaboniswa kuzo zombini imboniselo emfutshane, ethatha kuphela indawo encinane yecala lasekhohlo lekhusi, kwaye nemboniselo ende, ethatha icala lasekhohlo lekhusi kodwa iyakwazi ukubonisa iibhokisi zeposi ezininzi. Ungaqhobosha phakathi kwezi mboniselo zimbini phantsi kwe <guilabel
>Inkangeleko</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>Ubeko</guilabel
> kwi <guilabel
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guilabel
> incoko yababini. Kwakhona bona i <link linkend="folders"
>Icandelo Lencwadi ezineenkcukacha</link
> xa ufun aulwazi oluphangaleleyo malunga nendlela yokusebenzisa iincwadi ezineenkcukacha.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ulwahlulo lwe Headers (ulwahlulo lasekunene phezulu)</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Olu lwahlulo ludwelisa ulwazi lwe header (umyalezo Iindwe zeNdawo engatshintshiyo, Umthumeli, Umxholo, Umhla, obubodwa Ubungakanani neNqaku) yemiyalezo kwincwadi yangoku ekhethiweyo. Ukunqakraza kwi header kuzakukhetha lo myalezo kwaye iwubonise kulwahlulo loMyalezo. Ungakhetha kwakhona uthotho lwemiyalezo ngokunqakraza kumyalezo omnye, ibambe phantsi i <keycap
>Shift</keycap
> isitshixo, kwaye nokunqakraza komnye umyalezo. Imiyalezo emibini oyinqakrazileyo izakukhethwa, kunye neminye imiyalezo yonke ephakathi. Ngokubamba phantsi i &Ctrl; isitshixo ongasikhetha naliphi inani lemiyalezo ngaphandle kwale iphakathi. Ungalungisa imiyalezo ngokunqakrzaza kumhlathi onqwenela ukuwulungisa. Ukuba unqakraza kumhlathi omnye ngaphezulu nakanye, indlela yolungiso izakuqhobosha phakathi konyuko/ulwehlo. Ukuba unqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umxholo</guilabel
> umhlathi, ungaqhobosha ulungiso phakathi kwe <guilabel
>Umxholo</guilabel
> unyuko/ulwehlo ne <guilabel
>Indawo engatshintshiyo</guilabel
> unyuko/ulwehlo. Ngokufanayo, ukuba unqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umhla</guilabel
> umhlathi, ungaqhobosha ulungiso phakathi <guilabel
>Umhla</guilabel
> unyuko/ulwehlo ne <guilabel
>Umhla (Indlela yokuFika)</guilabel
> unyuko/ulwehlo.</para
> </listitem
