<sect1 id="the-composer-window">
<title
>Iwindow yomqambi</title>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window issetyenziswa ukubhala imiyalezo emitsha. Ingabheniswa kwi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
></menuchoice
> menu okanye kwi <guiicon
>uxwebhu</guiicon
> icon kwi <guilabel
>Umfundi wePosi</guilabel
> ibar yeqhosha le window. Ukuba awucwangcisanga indawo lyefayile yotyikityo lwakho kwaye une <guilabel
>Sebenzisa utyikityo kwifayile</guilabel
> ikhangelwe kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> tab ye <guilabel
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guilabel
> incoko yababini, uzakunikwa indawo yefayile yakho yotyikityo phambi kwe <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> iwindow ivula.</para>

<sect2 id="composing-a-message">
<title
>Iqamba umyalezo</title>

<para
>Ukubhala umyalezo wakho, gcwalisa imihlaba eyiyo kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window. Kukho ezahlukileyo iindlela ezimfutshane ukukunceda ukubhala imiyalezo yakho. I <guiicon
>ellipsis</guiicon
> amaqhiosha ecaleni kwe <guilabel
>Kwi:</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Cc:</guilabel
>, ne <guilabel
>Bcc:</guilabel
> imihlaba izakubiza incwadi yedilesi ukuze  ukhethe iidilesi apha.</para>

<para
>Xa uqala ukuchwetheza idilesi kwi <guilabel
>Kwi:</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>Cc:</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>Bcc:</guilabel
> imihlaba, i popup izakuvela enikeza iidilesi ezithelekisekayo ezisetyenziswe ngoku nedilesi ezithelekisekayo kweyakho incwadi yeedilesi. Qaphela ukuba olu gqibo-luzenzekelayo ngumzekelo-onovakalelo, ngoko ukuba uchwetheza i <guilabel
>john</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>John Doe &lt;doe@acme.com&gt;</guilabel
> akazukuza ngokuzenzekelayo. Ukuba awuyithandi ezenzekelayo i popup ungayikhubaza ngokunqakraza nge &RMB; kumhlaba kwaye khetha eyahlukileyo indlela yogqibo.</para>

<para
>Naxa ufuna ukudibanisa ngaphezu kwesinye somamkeli komnye wemihlaba, sebenzisa isiphumlisi ukwahlula idilesi nganye kwelandelayo. Ungafuna ukukhankanya iidilesi ezipheleleyo ezilungileyo (&ie; <userinput
>user@domain.com</userinput
>) nakubasebenzisi bobulali.</para>

<para
>Ungasebenzisa i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Imboniselo</guimenu
></menuchoice
> menu ukucwangcisa imihlaba ye header enikezwe kuwe. Xa ugqibile ngomyalezo wakho, betha i <guiicon
>Thumela</guiicon
> iqhosha (imvulophu) ukufola okanye thumela umyalezo. Ukuba awufuni ukuthumela umyalezo wakho, khetha <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Gcina kwincwadi yemizobo</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. </para
> 

</sect2>

<sect2 id="attachments">
<title
>Izifakelo</title>

<para
>Ungafakela iifayile kumyalezo wakho ngokusebenzisa enye kwindlela ezingezantsi:</para>

<itemizedlist
> <listitem
> <para
>Nqakraza i <guiicon
>uqhobosho lwephepha</guiicon
> iqhosha kwaye khetha ifayile onqwenela ukuyifakela.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Tsala ifayile kwi desktop okanye olunye ulawulo kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Khetha enye yeenketho kwi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Fakela</guimenu
></menuchoice
> menu.</para
> </listitem
> </itemizedlist>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Iimpahla zeQela loMyalezo</guilabel
> incoko yababini izakuvela ukukunika ulwazi malunga nofakelo lwakho. I &MIME;-udidi ne <guilabel
>Igama</guilabel
> imihlaba igcwaliswa ngokuzenzekelayo ngamaxabiso angawo. Ngamanye amaxesha i &MIME;-ixabiso lodidi lunoku ngalungi. Ungachwetheza nakweyiphi intsingiselo ye &MIME;-udidi okanye khetha kuluhlu leqhelekileyo i &MIME;-iididi. Ungakhetha kwakhona indlela ye enkhowudingi yefayile yakho kuluhlu lweenketho ze enkhowudingi (ngesiqhelo, ixabiso lokungagqibekanga lisebenza kakuhle).</para>

<para
>Xa ifayile ifakelelwe kumyalezo wakho, ivela kwi kulwahlulo Lwezifakelo ezantsi kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window. Ungasusa, ugcine, okanye ufumane ulwazi malunga nofakelo ngokukhetha igama layo kulwahlulo Lwezifakelo nokukhetha i <menuchoice
><guimenuitem
>Susa</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>, <menuchoice
><guimenuitem
>Gcina...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>, okanye <menuchoice
><guimenuitem
>Iimpahla...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> kwi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Fakela</guimenu
></menuchoice
> menu. </para>

<para
><application
>PGP</application
>/<application
>GnuPG</application
> izitshixo zingafakelwa kwakhona kumyalezo wakho ngokusebenzisa ezizezona iinketho kwi<menuchoice
><guimenu
>Fakela</guimenu
></menuchoice
> menu. <acronym
>PGP</acronym
> izifakelo ezingundoqo ziphathwa njengezifakelo zefayile.</para>

<!-- copied from below -->
<warning
><para
>Ungafihla imiyalezo yakho ethunyelwe nge &kmail;, kodwa oku akuthethi ukuba izifakelo zifihliwe. Uzakufihla izifakelo zakho encwadini, usebenzisa umyalelo weqokobhe okanye esinye isixhobo phambi kokufakela zona.</para
></warning>
