>ispell</application
> okanye <application
>aspell</application
> umkhangeli wopelo. Qaphela ukuba ungafuna ukuqwalasela umkhangeli wopelo usebenzisa i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Umkhangeli wopelo...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>.</para>

