<sect1 id="folders">
<title
>Iincwadi ezineenkcukacha zomyalezo</title>

<para
>Iincwadi ezineenkcukacha zisetyenziswa ukuqokelela imiyalezo yakho ye email. Ngokunga gqibekanga, zonke iincwadi zomyalezo zigcinwa kulawulo <filename class="directory"
>Iposi</filename
>, eyenziwe kulawulo lwakho lasekhaya. Xa uqala kuqala nge &kmail; i <guilabel
>ibhokisi yangaphakathi</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>ibhokisi yangaphandle</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>iposi-ethunyelweyo</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>umonakalo</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>imizobo</guilabel
> iincwadi ziyenziwa. Ezi ncwadi inye inemisebenzi ethile.</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>ibhokisi yangaphakathi:</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Apho i &kmail; ngokungagqibekanga ibeka imiyalezo yakho emitsha xa ucela yona ikhangele iposi yakho. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>ibhokisi yangaphandle:</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Apho imiyalezo ibekwa khona ukulinda ukusiwa. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>iposi-ethunyelweyo:</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iqulathe ukhuphelo lwayo yonke imiyalezo oyithumeleyo. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>umonakalo:</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iqulathe yonke imiyalezo oyicimeleyo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>imizobo:</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iqulathe imiyalezo oyiqalileyo ukuhlela kodwa engagqitywanga.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Ungafumanisa ukuba iincwadi ezisezantsi zilungele iimfuno zakho. Ngoko, noxa, uzakufuna iincwadi ukukunceda uqokelele imiyalezo yakho. Ukwenza incwadi entsha, khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Incwadi eneenkcukacha</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Yenza...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> Iwindow izakunikeza igama lencwadi eneenkcukacha. Ukuba awufuni ibekumphakamo ophezulu, ungakhetha incwadi phantsi kwalapho izakuvela khona. Ukuba ufuna ukutshintsha izicwangciso zencwadi eneenkcukacha, khetha incwadi onqwenela ukuyiguqula kancinane kulwahlulo Lweencwadi ezineenkcukacha kwaye khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Incwadi eneenkcukacha</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Iimpahla...</guimenuitem
> </menuchoice
>.</para>

<para
>Ukusa imiyalezo kwenye incwadi ukuya kwenye, khetha umyalezo(imi) ofuna ukuwusa kwaye cinezela i <keycap
>M</keycap
> isitshixo okanye khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Yise ku</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Uluhlu lwencwadi luzakuvela. Khetha incwadi kuluhlu ofuna ukusa imiyalezo kuyo. Imiyalezo ingasiwa ngokutsala kulwahlulo lwe Headers ukuya kulwahlulo lLwencwadi ezineenkcukacgha.</para>

<para
>Ukuba ufuna ukucacisa yonke imiyalezo ngaphandle kwencwadi khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Incwadi eneenkcukacha</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Engenanto</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Yonke imiyalezo kwincwadi ekhethiweyo izakusiwa kweyomonakalo. Ukuba incwadi ekhethiweyo yi <guilabel
>umonakalo</guilabel
> incwadi eneenkcukacha, yonke imiyalezo izakucinywa ngokupheleleyo.</para>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="the-address-book">
<title
>Incwadi yedilesi</title>

<para
>Incwadi yedilesi ikuvumela ugcine iidilesi ze email eziqhele ukusetyenziswa. Ungabiza incwadi yedilesi kwi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
></menuchoice
> menu, iqhosha lencwadi yedilesi kwengundoqo iwindow, okanye i <guiicon
>incwadi yedilesi</guiicon
> iqhosha kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window.</para>

<para
>Ungakhetha phakathi kweendidi ezahlukileyo zeencwadi zedilesi kwi <guilabel
>Inkangeleko</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>Idilesi yencwadi</guilabel
> icandelo kwi &kmail;'s <guilabel
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guilabel
> incoko yababini.</para>

<para
>Incwadi yedilesi engagqibekanga yi &kaddressbook;, ene <ulink url="help:/kaddressbook"
>iuxwebhu layo</ulink
>.</para>

<sect2 id="the-address-book-simple">
<title
>&kmail;ilula <quote
>ngokwakwantu</quote
> incwadi yedilesi</title>

<para
>Ukudibanisa iidilesi kwncwadi yedilesi, chwetheza idilesi ye email kwicandelo elisezantsi lwe window kwaye betha i <guibutton
>Dibanisa</guibutton
> iqhosha. Idilesi izakuvela phezulu koluhlu (ixesha elizayo uvula incwadi yedilesi izakuba nendawo yayo ngokwendlela yo nobumba). Ukususa idilesi, yikhethe kuluhlu kwaye betha i <guibutton
>Susa</guibutton
> iqhosha. </para>

<para
>Iidilesi zingadityaniswa kwakhona kwincwadi yedilesi kwi <guilabel
>Umfundi wePosi</guilabel
> window ngu &RMB; unqakraza kwidilesi ye email kwi <guilabel
>Kwi:</guilabel
> okanye <guilabel
>Kwi:</guilabel
> mihlaba kwaye ikhetha i <guilabel
>Dibanisa incwadi yedilesi</guilabel
>.</para>

</sect2>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="filters">
<title
>Amacebo okucoca ulwelo</title>
<anchor id="filters-id"/>

<para
>Emva kokusebenzisa i &kmail; ixesha elithile, ungafumana ukuba unengxaki yokulungisa imiyalezo emitsha kwibhokisi yakho yangaphakathi xa zifika. Amacebo okucoca akuvumela wenze ngokuzenzekelayo iintshukumo ezithile kwimiyalezo engenayo nokwenza iintshukumo ngokwencwadi kwimiyalezo ekhethiweyo kwincwadi eneenkcukacha.</para>

<para
>Amacebo okucoca aqulathe umlinganiselo wokuphendla, onemithetho yayo esetyenziswa njenge nto yokugweba ukwenza noba eli cebo linokufakwa kumyalezo onikiweyo, noluhlu lweentshukumo zecebo lokucoca, ezichaza okwenziwayo nge okanye kumyalezo ukuba umlinganiselo wophendlo uyathelekiseka. Funda ngaphezulu malunga nemilinganiselo neentshukumo zecebo lokucoca kula macandelo asezantsi alandelayo.</para>

<caution
><para
> Amacebo aqwalaselwa elinye emva kwelinye, uqala ngelokuqala kuluhlu. Elokuqala elinomlinganiselo othelekisekayo nomyalezo onikiweyo uyaphunyezwa. Ungacela ukuba amacebo asaleleyo anokufakwa nawo, kodwa okungagqibekanga kukumisa uqhubekeko kwicebo elithelekisekayo. </para
></caution>

<para
>Ngesiqhelo, amacebo asetyenziswa kwimiyalezo engenayo, kodwa angafakwa kumyalezo okanye iqela lemiyalezo. Kwimiyalezo yecebo lokucoca elikhethiweyo, khetha imiyalezo ofuna ukuyicoca nokuyichwetheza <keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>J</keycap
></keycombo
> okanye khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Faka Amacebo okucoca</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Oku kuzakufaka wonke amacebo wakho okucoca kulo miyalezo; akukho ndlela yakufaka kuphela amacebo okucoca athile kwimiyalezo, ngaphandle kwemiyalezo engenayo nephumayo.</para>

<sect2 id="filter-quick">
<title
>Ukwenziwa kweCebo lokucoca Elikhawulezayo</title>

<para
>Kukho iindlela ezimbini zokwenza icebo lokucoca: Indlela ekhawulezayo kukusebenzisa i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Yenza Icebo Lokucoca</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Oku kuzakubiza incoko yababini yecebo lokucoca kwaye ikunike elitsha icebo elinomthetho wokuqala womlinganiselo wophendlo nentshukumo yokuqala (njenge <quote
>yiya kwincwadi eneenkcukacha</quote
>) beka kuqala. Kwimizekelo emininzi, konke omele ukwenze kukukhetha incwadi apho umyalezo uzakusiwa khona. Kodwa ungakwazi, kunjalo, hlela icebo njengoko uthanda.</para>

<para
>Into enika umdla malunga nale ndlela kukuba ukwenza icebo lokucoca kuluhlu lokuposa lizakuzama ngenene nzima ukufumana i header eqwalasela kanye iiposi kolo luhlu. Ukuba iyaphumelela, igama elithekelelwayo loluhlu linikwa kwi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guisubmenu
>Yenza icebo lokucoca</guisubmenu
><guimenuitem
>Icebo lokucoca ku luhlu-lokuposa...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> ungeno lwe menu.</para>

<tip
><para
>Kwimizekelo emininzi oku kuyasebenza kakuhle, ngamanye amaxesha ungacima amaqela emixholo ye header azakutshintsha kwakhona. Ngesiqhelo, ukugcina nje idilesi yoluhlu kuyasebenza ngcono.</para
></tip>

<para
>Indlela yesibini kukulungisa icebo lokucoca ekuqaleni ngoku biza incoko yababini yecebo lokucoca ngapha kwe <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Qwalasela Amacebo okucoca...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Incoko yababini yecebo lokucoca ichazwe ngokwenkcukacha kwicandelo elisezantsi elilandelayo.</para>
</sect2>

<sect2 id="filter-dialog">
<title
>Incoko yababini Yecebo lokucoca</title>
<anchor id="filter-dialog-id"/>

<para
>Oku kukuvumela ukuba uphathe kwaye uhlele uluhlu lwakho lwamacebo okucoca.</para>

<para
>Ufikelele kuyo noba ugqitha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guisubmenu
>Yenza Icebo lokucoca</guisubmenu
></menuchoice
> okanye <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Imithetho Yecebo lokucoca...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>.</para>

<para
>Ukukhupha le ncoko yababini ngaphandle kokufaka utshintsho, nqakraza kwi <guibutton
>Cima</guibutton
> okanye betha &Esc;.</para>

<para
>Incoko yababini yahlulwe kumacandelo angundoqo amane:</para>
<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Amacebo ococo lolwelo akhoyo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Iqela liqulathe uluhlu lwamacebo okucoca namaqhosha entshukumo ukuguqula kancinane amacebo okucoca, ngamagama ukwenza amacebo okucoca amatsha, ukuwasa phezulu okanye ezantsi kuluhlu, okanye ukucima nokuwanika amagama kwakhona. Ukuba ukhetha icebo lokucoca kuluhlu, iimpahla zazo ziboniswa kwicala lesandla-sasekunene sencoko yababini.</para
></listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Into ethathwa njengegweba icebo lokucoca ulwelo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Kweli qela ungahlela umlinganiselo omawuthelekiswe yimiyalezo yecebo lokucoca emalifakwe kubo. Ungakhetha apha noba yonke yonke imithetho echaziweyo emayithelekiswe okanye noba izimamva ezinokuthelekiswa nabani na kubo. Bona <link linkend="filter-criteria"
>Phendla Imilinganiselo</link
> ngezantsi yenkcazelo eneenkcukacha yodidi ngalunye lophendlo.</para
> <para
> You can click on <guibutton
>More</guibutton
> to get an additional (initially empty) rule if you want to define more complex patterns and on <guibutton
>Fewer</guibutton
> to remove the last rule. <guibutton
>Clear</guibutton
> clears the pattern, &ie; it removes all but two rules from screen and resets those two.</para
> <para
>Engasebenziyo okanye engenanto imithetho ayihluzwa. Ngenene, iyasuswa ngaphakathi. Noba umthetho onikiweyo uqwalaselwa ngokungasebenzi kuxhomekeke kudidi lomthetho, kodwa njengomthetho wobhontsi ungacinga ukuba imithetho iqwalaselwa ngokungasebenzi ukuba ithambeka (eyokuqala ibhokisi yesibini kumqolo ngamnye) okanye umtya wophendlo (uhlelo lwelayini kwisiphelo somqolo ngamnye) alunanto. Ngoko, ukucima ngesiphumo  umthetho othile, ufuna kuphela eyona ingenanto yalo mihlaba mibini yohlelo.</para
></listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Iintshukumo zecebo lokucoca ulwelo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Kweli qela ungahlela uluhlu lweentshukumo olufakwa kuyo yonke imiyalezo ethelekiseka nomlinganiselo ochaziweyo wophendlo. Bona <link linkend="filter-action"
>Iintshukumo zecebo lokucoca</link
> ngezantsi zenkcazelo eneenkcukacha zodidi lwentshukumo ngalunye.</para
> <para
> Unganqakraza kwi <guibutton
>Ngaphezulu</guibutton
> ukufumana entsha, engenanto intshukumo ukuba ufuna ukuchaza ngaphezulu kwenye intshukumo kunye ne <guibutton
>Mbalwa</guibutton
> ukusyusa intshukumo yokugqibela. <guibutton
>Cacisa</guibutton
> icacisa uluhlu, &ie; isusa konke kodwa intshukumo enye kwaye icwangcisa kwakhona leyo.</para
> <para
>Ezingasebenziyo okanye ezingenanto iintshukumo aziphunyezwanga. Ngenene, zisuswa ngaphakathi. Noba intshukumo enikiweyo iqwalaselwa ngokungasebenzi kuxhomekeke kudidi lwentshukumo, kodwa njengomthetho wobhontsi ungacinga ukuba iintshukumo ziqwalaselwa ngokungabinanto ukuba akukho didi lukhethiweyo okanye - kumzekelo weentshukumo ezifuna iparameter yokubhaliweyo (&ie; enye ekufuneka ingenisiweyo kuhlelo lwelayini) -iparameter ayinanto. Ngoko, ukucima ngesiphumo intshukumo ethile, ufuna kuphela ukungacwangcisi olwayo udidi, &ie; khetha eyokugqibela (engenanto) umba kudidi lwebhokisi yesibini.</para
></listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Iinketho zaphambili</guilabel
></term
><listitem
><para
> Kweli qela ungachaza iinketho ezimbalwa zaphambili zamacebo okucoca, ezikuvumela ukucola ucoco lwakho.</para
> <para
>Usebenzisa le bhokisi yesibini, ungaqhobosha ufako lwecebo lokucoca elihambelanayo: I <guilabel
>engenayo</guilabel
> ukhetho lubonisa ukuba inokuqwalaselelwa iiposi ezingenayo (&ie; kwi <guimenuitem
>Khangela Iposi</guimenuitem
>), ngexesha i <guilabel
>ephumayo</guilabel
> ukhetho lubonisa eziphumayo iiposi (&ie; kwi <guimenuitem
>Thumela</guimenuitem
>).</para
> <note
><para
>Qaphela ukuba akwenzeki ngoku ukuchaza icebo lokucoca olungaqwalaselwanga lwencwadi yokucoca. Lo ngumda owaziwayo. </para
></note
></listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<note
><para
>Amacebo okucoca anikwa amagama ngokuzenzekelayo ngaphandle kokuwanika amagama usebenzisa i <guibutton
>Nika igama kwakhona...</guibutton
> iqhosha. Incoko yababini icinga ukuba izakuqhubeka ngokunika igama-ngokuzenzekelayo icebo lokucoca nje ukuba igama lecebo liqale nge <quote
>&lt;</quote
>. </para
></note>

<para
>Nqakraza kwi <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> iqhosha ukufaka lonke utshintsho kwaye uvale incoko yababini, <guibutton
>Faka</guibutton
> ukufaka lonke utshintsho nokushiya incoko yababini ivuliwe, ne <guibutton
>Cima</guibutton
> ukuvala incoko yababini ngaphandle kokufaka naluphi na utshintsho.</para>

<note
> <para
> Ukuba ufaka utshintsho lwecebo lokucoca, &ie; ugqitha <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> okanye <guibutton
>Faka</guibutton
>, kuphela asebenzayo amacebo okucoca akhutshelweyo ngaphakathi kumphathi wecebo lokucoca.</para
> <para
>Icebo lokucoca lithathwa njengelingasebenziyo ukuba</para
> <orderedlist
> <listitem
><para
>umlinganiselo wophendlo uqulathe imithetho engenanto okanye</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
>uluhlu lwentshukumo alunanto.</para
></listitem
> </orderedlist
> <para
>Ngokufanayo, imithetho engenanto neentshukumo iyasuswa kumlinganiselo kunye noluhlu lwentshukumo, phambi kokuba icebo lokucoca ligcinwe.</para
> </note>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="filter-criteria">
<title
>Phendla Imilinganiselo</title>

<para
>Umsebenzi oqhelekileyo wamacebo okucoca kumthumeli wemiyalezo. Oku kunokwenziwa ngokukhetha i <guilabel
>Kwi</guilabel
>. Ubhejo olulungileyo loluhlu lokuposa luzakuba yi <guilabel
>&lt;Ku okanye Cc&gt;</guilabel
>. Kodwa kukho ezinye ezithathwa njengesigwebo icebo lokucoca elingaziphendlayo:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>&lt;umyalezo&gt;</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iphendla umyalezo wonke (&ie; headers, umzimba nezifakelo, ukuba zikhona).</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>&lt;umzimba&gt;</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iphendla umzimba womyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>&lt;nayiphi iheader&gt;</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iphendla iiheder zomyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>&lt;Ku okanye Cc&gt;</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iphendla i <quote
>Ku</quote
> ne <quote
>Cc</quote
> imihlaba ye header yomyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>&lt;ubungakanani&gt;</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Icwangcisa imida ephezulu nesezantsi yobungakanani bomyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>&lt;ubudala kwiintsuku&gt;</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Icwangcisa imida ephezulu nesezantsi yobudala bomyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Nawuphi na omnye umtya</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iphendla umhlaba we header onikwe ngulo mtya.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="filter-action">
<title
>Intshukumo yecebo lokucoca</title>

<para
>Usebenziso oluqhelekileyo lecebo kukulungisa imiyalezo engenayo kwiincwadi ezineenkcukacha ezithile. Oku kunokwenziwa ngokukhetha i <guilabel
>yiya kwincwadi eneenkcukacha</guilabel
>. Nalu uluhlu lweentshukumo ezinokwenzeka:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>yiya kwincwadi eneenkcukacha</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kuzakusa umyalezo kwenye incwadi eneenkcukacha. Eyangoku ayinaku sebenzisa <acronym
>IMAP</acronym
> iincwadi ezinenkcukacha njengetekeni.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>phawula njenge</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kukuvumela ukuphawula umyalezo njengofundo okanye okubalulekileyo (enendwe), kodwa kwakhona isiwe phambili, yaphendulwa, &etc;</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>cwangcisa inkcaza ku</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kuzakucwangcisa <emphasis
>eyakho</emphasis
> uqwalaselo ukuba uphendula kulo myalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>cwangcisa uthutho ku</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kuzakucwangcisa indlela yezithuthi (&eg; <acronym
>SMTP</acronym
>) ukuba uphendula kumyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>cwangcisa Impendulo-Ku ku</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Izakuguqula kancinane i <guilabel
>Phendula-Ku</guilabel
> umhlaba walo myalezo. Oku kunokuba luncedo kuluhlu loposo olucwangcisa ngokuzenzekelayo Phendula-Ku ongayithandiyo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>yise phambili ku</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Izakusa phambili umyalezo kwenye idilesi ye email.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>yibonise kwakhona ku</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Izakubonisa kwakhona umyalezo kwenye idilesi ye email.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>ijikile/ibuyiselwe</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Izakuzama ukubuyisela umyalezo kumthumeli njengoku ngaphahtelwanga.</para
> <caution
><para
>Oku kuzakusebenzakuphela ukuba idilesi yomthumeli ye email iyasebenza. Yi <emphasis
>hayi</emphasis
> umzekelo we spam ezininzi.</para
></caution
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>qinisekisa uphathelo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
><para
>Izakuzama ukubuyisela umyalezo kumthumeli owalathisa ngempumelelo uphathelo lomyalezo wakhe okanye wakhe.</para
> <para
>Le ntshukumo ikuvumela ukhethe ozakufumana iirisiti zophathelo kuwe. Noxa ungenza uqinisekiso lothumelo lophathelo kwi <guilabel
>Qwalasela &kmail;...</guilabel
> incoko yababini (icandelo <guilabel
>Ukhuseleko</guilabel
>) siyaleza ukungazithumeli kuwo wonke umntu, ukusukela ukuba oku kwenza uphawulo lwe &eg; spam ilula kakhulu kumthumeli.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>susa iheader</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Izakususa <emphasis
>zonke</emphasis
>imihlaba ye header ngegama elinikwe kum,yalezo. Oku kuluncedo kakhulu ekususeni i bogus <quote
>Phendula-Ku:</quote
> iiheader.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>dibanisa iheader</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ukuba akukho mhlaba sele ukhona, izakudibanisa umhlaba omtsha we header ethunyelweyo ngegama elinikiweyo nexabiso kumyalezo. Ukuba sele kukho kukho umhlaba we header onelo gama, ibhalwe ngaphezulu ngelitsha(eli nikoweyo) ixabiso. Ukuba sele kukho iiheader ezininzi ezinegama elinikiweyo (&eg; <quote
>Yamkelwe:</quote
>iiheader), engenasizathu yazo ibhalwe ngaphezulu kwaye ezinye zishiywe zingatshintshanga. Oku ngu mda owaziwayo. Ungafuna ukudibanisa eli cebo nge <guilabel
>susa iheader</guilabel
> icebo lokucoca ukuqinisekisa ukuba akukho ezinye iiheader ezinelo gama kumyalezo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>bhala kwakhona iheader</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Izakuvavanya umhlaba onikiweyo we header, guqula kancinane imixholo yawo kwaye uyibhale ngemva. Umtya wokuphendla usoloko utolikwa njengomzekelo-onovakalelo wochazo lwarhoqo. Umtya wobuyiselo ufakwe ngokufundekayo ngaphandle kwezenzeko ze <userinput
>\n</userinput
>, <userinput
>$n</userinput
> ne <userinput
>${nn}</userinput
>, apho <userinput
>n</userinput
> iyengakhabiyo (isuntswana-elilodwa, ngaphandle kwendlela yesithathu) inani okanye <userinput
>0</userinput
>. Ezi zilungiso zitolikwa njengentelekiso ezisemva kwimitya esezantsi ebanjwe ngegama elikumtya wophendlo.</para
><para
>Imida engqongo njengakwi <guilabel
>dibanisa iheader</guilabel
> intshukumo iyafakwa apha, nayo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>phumeza umyalelo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kuzakuphumeza udweliso lwenkqubo, kodwa aluzukuguqula kancinane umyalezo. Khankanya umendo opheleleyoi kudweliso lwenkqubo ofuna ukuluphumeza. &kmail; izakuvala lude lube udweliso lwenkqubo luyabuyiselwa. Ungalutyisa udweliso lwenkqubo ngamaqela eposi: <symbol
>&percnt;0</symbol
>, <symbol
>&percnt;1</symbol
>, &etc; izakumela iifayile ezimele amaqela omyalezo. Eposi eqhelekileyo <symbol
>&percnt;0</symbol
> koku bhaliweyo, <symbol
>&percnt;1</symbol
> ufakelo lokuqala njalo-njalo. Ngokudibeneyo, umyalezo wonke utyiswe kudweliso lwenkqubo ye <acronym
>stdin</acronym
>.</para
> <caution
><para
>Oku kusebenza ngoku ukuba umyalezo une <emphasis
>noko enye</emphasis
> ufakelo. Hayi, noba <symbol
>&percnt;0</symbol
> izakusebenza kumzekelo ngokubanzi!</para
></caution
> <tip
><para
> Ungafaka imiyalelo yeqokobhe enegama apha, ukusukela ukuba i &kmail; isebenzisa iqokobhe elisezantsi ukuphumeza ilayinim yomyalelo. Ngoko ke, noba lo myalelo uzakusebenza (kwimida yayo): <userinput
><command
>uudecode</command
> <option
>-o</option
> <parameter
>$(mktemp kmail-uudecoded.XXXXXX)</parameter
> &amp;&amp; <command
>echo</command
> <parameter
>$'\a'</parameter
></userinput
></para
></tip
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>umbhobho ngaphaya</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kuzakutyisa umyalezo wodweliso lwenkqubo. Ukuba olo dweliso lwenkqubo lubuyisela imveliso, umyalezo wangoku (uquka iiheader) izakubuyiselwa ngale mveliso. Ukuba udweliso lwenkqubo alubuyiseli mveliso, umyalezo awuzukutshintsha. Khankanya umendo opheleleyo wodweliso lwenkqubo.</para
> <caution
><para
>Lumka ngale ntshukumo, njengoko izakonakalisa eyakho imiyalezo ukuba udweliso lwenkqubo yecebo lokucoca lubuyisela inkunkuma okanye iilayini ezingaphezulu.</para
></caution
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="filter-examples">
<title
>Imizekelo yecebo lokucoca</title>

<para
>Ukuba ndinikelwe kwi (ngokubanzi) &kde; Uluhlu, Ndizakwenza incwadi eneenkcukacha yoluhlu (Ndizakuyibiza ngo <replaceable
>KDE-Ngokubanzi</replaceable
>) kwaye sebenzisa icebo lokucoca ukunikeza ngokuzenzekelayo imiyalezo emitsha kwibhokisi yam yangaphakathi ukuya kweyam i <replaceable
>KDE-Ngokubanzi</replaceable
> incwadi eneenkcukacha ukuba zisuka kwi &kde; Uluhlu. Apha kulapho unenza khona icebo lokucoca:</para>

<procedure
> <title
>Icoca uluhlu lokuposa</title
> <step
> <para
>Zama ukuba <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guisubmenu
>Yenza icebo lokucoca</guisubmenu
><guimenuitem
>Icebo ku Luhlu-lokuposa...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> ingaqwalasela uluhlu lokuposa (igama loluhlu lizakuvela ngoku kumba we menu). Kulo mzekelo, oku kuyasebenza kwaye ndinikwe icebo lokucoca eline <quote
>X-Uluhlu-lokuposa <guilabel
>ilingana ne</guilabel
> &lt;kde@lists.netcentral.net&gt;</quote
