<sect1 id="pgp">
<!-- This section is from Andreas Gungl, 2000-05-21 -->
<title
><application
>Ikhusi Elilungileyo Elihle</application
> (<application
>PGP</application
>) / <application
>GNU Ukhuselo Lekhusi</application
> (<application
>GnuPG</application
>)</title>

<para
>Oku kukwazisa okufutshane kokucwangcisa i &kmail;'s <application
>PGP</application
> inkxaso. Izakunika othsuphe abathile kusebenziso lwe <application
>PGP</application
> nayo. Ibhalelwe abantu abaqalayo kule ariya. Ukuba uyalazi usebenziso lwe <acronym
>PGP</acronym
>, ungatsiba amanqwanqwa amaninzi. Olu xwebhu (kunye ne &kmail; ujongano lomsebenzisi) ithetha ngokubanzi kuphela malunga ne <quote
>PGP</quote
>, kodwa ifaka kuzo zombini <application
>PGP</application
> ne <application
>GnuPG</application
>, noxa ezinye <application
>GnuPG</application
> iiparameter zelayini yomyalelo zinokuba nomahluko.</para>

<para
>Nceda khangela kwakhona phandle i <link linkend="pgp-faq"
>&FAQ; umba malunga <application
>PGP</application
></link
>.</para>

<warning
><para
>Ungafihla imiyalezo yakho ethunyelwe nge &kmail;, kodwa oku akuthethi ukuba izifakelo zifihliwe. Uzakufihla izifakelo zakho encwadini, usebenzisa umyalelo weqokobhe okanye esinye isixhobo phambi kokufakela zona.</para
></warning>

<warning
><para
>&kmail; izakuxhomekeka kwi <application
>PGP</application
>'s imveliso. Le mveliso yahluka rhoqo phakathi koguqulelo olwahlukileyo lwe <application
>PGP</application
>, ngoko kubalulekile ukuba uyavavanya ukuba ufihlo lusebenza ngenene ngocwangciso lwakho phambi kokuqala ukuyisebenzisa ngokuzimiseleyo. &kmail; inoku <emphasis
>hayi</emphasis
> iyakulumkisa ukuba kukho into engaphumeleliyo. Kungcono wenze <guilabel
>Bonisa okubhaliweyo okufihliweyo emva kokuqamba</guilabel
>. </para
></warning>

<para
>Ukucwangcisa nokusebenzisa <application
>PGP</application
> inkxaso kwi &kmail; kuyimfuneko ukuba ne <application
>PGP</application
> efakiweyo necwangciswe kakuhle. Kunjalo asinakukunika ulwaziso olupheleleyo lwe <application
>PGP</application
> apha. Sizakukhankanya kuphela amanqwanqwa omawuwenze ukufumana i <application
>PGP</application
> ihamba. Kwinkcukacha uzakujonga kwesemagqabini i <application
>PGP</application
> uxwebhu okanye <ulink url="http://www.gnupg.org/docs.html#guides"
>I GNU Incwadi yesandla yeKhusi</ulink
>.</para
> 

<para
>Yingcamango elungileyo ukufunda eli xwebhu njengo kwazisa kuwonke-wonke ufihlo olungundoqo (&eg; ngaphandle kwe <application
>PGP</application
> 6.5.x package). Apho ungafunda okuninzi malunga nezimaphambili ezingundoqo, ezizakukunceda uqonde okwenzekayo. Nako, imiba emininzi yokhuseleko omawuyazi ixoxwa apha.</para>

<para
>Ngoku masiqale.</para>

<sect2 id="pgp-preconditions">
<title
>Iimeko eziphambili</title>

<para
>&kmail; ilindela ukuba esakho <application
>PGP</application
> okubini kubizwa ngokuba <command
>pgp</command
>. Kumzekelo we <application
>GnuPG</application
>, ilindela okubini kubizwe <command
>gpg</command
>. Ukuba asingomzekelo wakho, yenza nje i symlink.</para>

<para
>Ukuba awukwenzanga oko, uzakujikelezisa izitshixo ezimbini (imfihlo ne sitshixo sikawonke-wonke) yoqwalaselo lwakho. Kufuneka wenze oku kwilayini yomyalelo (sebenzisa i <userinput
><command
>pgp</command
> <option
>-kg</option
></userinput
>). &kmail; ayinankxaso yangaphakathi ye <application
>pgp</application
>'s ujikeleziso lwesitshixo ngeli xesha. Uqwalasdelo (iqhele ukub aligama lakho lilandelwa yidilesi yakho ye email kwizigweqi, enjenge <userinput
>John Doe &lt;john@example.com&gt;</userinput
>) nebinzana lakho logqithiso abalulekile kusebe-nziswano phakathi kwe &kmail; ne <application
>pgp</application
>.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="pgp-settings">
<title
><application
>PGP</application
> Izicwangciso Ezizalanayo kwi &kmail;</title>

<para
>Ngenisa eyakho <application
>PGP</application
> uqwalaselo lomsebenzisi kumhlaba wohambelwano lwe <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> izicwangciso. Ngokuy khetha i <guilabel
>PGP</guilabel
> tab kwi <guilabel
>Ukhuseleko</guilabel
> iphepha lezicwangciso. Apho uzakufumana iinketho ezilandelayo:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Gcina ibinzana logqitho kwinkumbulo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Xa olu khetho lucimile, &kmail; izakucela ibinzana lakho logqitho ixesha ngalinye utyikitya umyalezo (phambi kokuthumela) okanye khetha umyalezo ofihliweyo. Ukub auqala olu khetho, &kmail; izakukhumbula elakho ibinzana logqitho emva kwegalelo lakho lokuqala elinempumelelo ude ube ugqiba eyakho i &kmail; intlanganiso. Ibinzana logqitho ligcinwa kwinkumbulo kwaye ayibhalwa kwi harddiski.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Soloko ufihla kuyo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ukub aolu khetho lucimile kwaye ufuna ukuthumela umyalezo ofihliweyo komnye umntu, ngoku awunakufunda lo myalezo nakanye emva kokuba uqambe kwaye wayifihla. Qala olu khetho ukugcina imiyalezo ethunyelwe ifihliwe efundekayo kuwe.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Bonisa okubhaliweyo okufihliweyo emva kokuqamba</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kuzakubonisa iziphumo zofihlo kwaye zityikitya phambi kokuba umyalezo ufumane uthumelo. Le ndlela ungacima uthumelo ukuba ufihlo aluphumelelanga. Yaziswa ngamandla ukusebenzisa olu khetho.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Isixhobo sofihlo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Apha ungakhetha ukuba ufuna ukusebenzisa i <application
>PGP</application
>, <application
>GnuPG</application
> okanye akukho zixhobo zecomputer zofihlo nakanye. Kunjalo udweliso lwenkqubo olukhethayo luzakufakwa kwindlela yakho. Kubalulekile kwakhona ukukhetha uguqulelo kolunye ulwimi olululo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> tab ungakhangela kwakhona i <guilabel
>Tyikitya ngokuzenzekelayo imiyalezo usebenzisa i PGP</guilabel
> ukhetho. Oku kuthetha ukuba yonke imiyalezo yakho izakutyikitywa phambi kokuthunyelwa. (Ngoko awunakucwangcisa ukhetho lotyikityo lomyalezo ngamnye wencwadi.)</para>

<para
>Ngoku uyakwazi ukutyikitya imiyalezo ephumayo. Ukuvumela abantu bakuthumele imiyalezo efihliweyo kwaye ubavumele baqinisekise utyikityo lwakho kufuneka ubathumele isitshixo sakho sikawonke-wonke okanye ulayishe ngentla isitshixo sikawonke-wonke kwi <application
>PGP</application
> umncedisi wesitshixo ukuze babenokuthatha isitshixo sakho apho. Ukuthumela iiposi ezifihliweyo kwabanye abantu okanye ukuqinisekisa imiyalezo yabo etyikityiweyo uzakufuna izitshixo zabo zikawonke-wonke. Ungagcina esakho isitshixo(izi) kwekawonke-wonke <application
>PGP</application
> umncedisi wesitshixo onjenge <ulink url="http://www.cam.ac.uk.pgp.net/pgpnet/"
>http://www.cam.ac.uk.pgp.net/pgpnet/</ulink
>.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="pgp-sign-your-messages">
<title
>Tyikitya imiyalezo yakho</title>

<para
>Uqamba umyalezo wakho njngesiqhelo kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window ye &kmail;. Phambi kokuba uthumele umyalezo, khangela iqhosha ngeyenza umgca ngaphantsi i icon kuyo kwi bar yesixhobo yewindow yomqambi. Ngoku, ungathumela umyalezo. Uku yityikitya, &kmail; ifuna ukwazi esakho i <application
>PGP</application
> ibinzana logqitho. Ukuba awukhethanga i <guilabel
>Gcina ibinzana logqitho kwinkumbulo</guilabel
> kwi <guilabel
>Ukhuseleko</guilabel
> izicwangciso tab, &kmail; izakucela yona. Kwesinye isandla, ukuba sele unike ibinzana kwi &kmail;, izakutyikitya umyalezo ngaphandle konikezo naluphi olusa phambili.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="pgp-send-your-public-key">
<title
>Thumela Isitshixo sakho Sikawonke-wonke</title>

<para
>Lungisa umyalezo kumntu ofuna ukuthumela kuye isitshixo sakho sikawonke-wonke. Ngoku khetha kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window's menu <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Fakela</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Fakela Esam Isitshixo Sikawonke- wonke</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Oku kuzakufakela esakho isitshixo sikawonke-wonke kwiposi. Ngoku ungathumela iposi.</para>

<para
>Khumbula ukuba akukhuselekanga ukuba utyikitya umyalezo ukuqinisekisa ukuba umamkeli uzakufumana isitshixo esisiso. Kungakho umntu-ku-hlaselo-laphakathi, njengomnye umntu ongatshintsha isitshixo kwaye atyikitye umyalezo ngesinye isitshixo. Yilo nto umamkeli kufuneka aqinisekise isitshixo esifakelweyo ngokukhangela iminwe yesitshixo ngokuchasene nanako kwinndlela ekhuselekileyo kuwe. Jonga kwi <application
>PGP</application
> uxwebhu lwenkcukacha ezisa phambili.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="pgp-you-got-an-encrypted-message">
<title
>Unoiimyaslezo ofihlakeleyo</title>

<para
>Konke omawukwenze kukukhetha umyalezo kwi &kmail;. Uzakunikezwa ngebinzana lakho logqitho. Ngoku &kmail; izakuzama ukungafihli myalezo kwaye ikubonise okubhalioweyo okungenanto ukuba umyalezo ubufihliwe ngesitshixo sakho sikawonke-wonke. (Ukuba akunjalo, ngoku awuzukwazi ukuyifunda.) &kmail; igcina imiyalezo ifihliwe, ngoko akukho mntu unokufunda le miyalezo ngaphandle kokwazi ibinzana lakho logqitho.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="pgp-receiving-a-public-key">
<title
>Yamkela Isitshixo sikawonke-wonke</title>

<para
>Ungamkela isitshixo sikawonke-wonke njengofakelo okanye gqitha i http, ftp okanye i floppy. Phambi kokuba usebenzise esi sitshixo ukufihla umyalezo kumnini wesitshixo, uzakuqinisekisa isitshixo (khangela iminwe yayo okanye jonga izityikityo ezithembakeleyo). Ngoku ungadibanisa esi sitshixo kweyakhokawonke-wonke iringi yesitshixo ngokuchwetheza <userinput
><command
>pgp</command
> <option
>-ka</option
> <replaceable
>igama lefayile</replaceable
></userinput
> kwilayini yomyalelo ukuba usebenzisa i <application
>PGP</application
> or by typing <userinput
><command
>gpg</command
> <option
>--rhweba ngaphakathi</option
> <replaceable
>filename</replaceable
></userinput
> kwilayini yomyalelo ukuba usebenzisa i <application
>GnuPG</application
>. Ukuba isitshixo asiqinisekiswanga ngotyikityo oluthembakeleyo kwaye usebenzisa i <application
>PGP</application
>, awunakuyisebenzisa nge &kmail; ukufihla imiyalezo ngaphandle kokuba utyikitye eso sitshixo (sebenzisa i <userinput
><command
>pgp</command
> <option
>-ks</option
> <replaceable
>uqalaselo lwesitshixo</replaceable
></userinput
>). Nge <application
>GnuPG</application
>, kwesinye isandla, okwangoku kuyenzeka ukufihla imiyalezo ngezitshixo ezingathembakalanga.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="pgp-encrypt-your-messages">
<title
>Sebenzisa izitshixo zikawonke-wonke zabanye abantu - Fihla Imiyalezo yakho</title>

<para
>Ukuthumela umyalezo ofihliweyo komnye umntu onesitshixo sakhe sikawonke- wonke, wenza ngokulula umyalezo kwi window yomqambi. Phambi kokuthumela umyalezo; khangela iqhosha ngophawu lokutshixa kwi bar yesitshixo se window yomqambi. Ngoku thumela umyalezo.</para>

<para
>&kmail; isoloko isebenzisa isitshixo sokuqala esithelekiseka nedilesi yomamkeli ukufihla umyalezo. Ukuba i &kmail; ingafumana isitshixo esithelekisekayo somamkeli, izakubonisa uluhlu oluqulathe zonke izitshixo ezikhoyo. Ungakhetha isitshixo esisiso kuluhlu okanye cima intshukumo. &kmail; ingakwazisa malunga neemposiso ngapha wenkqubo yofihlo.</para>

<para
>Njengoko kukhankanyiwe ngasentla, awunakwazi ukufunda iiposi zakho ezifihliweyo ukuba awukhangeli i <guilabel
>Soloko ufihla kuyo</guilabel
> kwisicwangciso <guilabel
>Ukhuseleko</guilabel
> tab.</para>

</sect2>

</sect1>
</chapter>

