>Icwangcisa ityala lakho</link
> icandelo.</para>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="appearance-tab">
<title
>Isithuba senkangeleko</title>

<sect2 id="appearance-tab-fonts">
<title
>Imigca</title>

<para
>Eli candelo likuvumela utshintshe udidi, ubungakanani neqela labasebenzi bemigca yokubonisa. <guilabel
>Umzimba womyalezo</guilabel
> icwangcisa umgca yazo zombini ulwahlulo lomfundi ne window yomqambi. Kukho ungeno olwahlukileyo lwe <guilabel
>Uluhlu loMyalezo - Umhlaba Womhla</guilabel
> ngoko ungakhetha isithuba esinye somgca somhlaba womhla sofundo olungcono.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="appearance-tab-colors">
<title
>Imibala</title>

<para
>Eli candelo likuvumela utshintshe umbala wokubhaliweyo. <guilabel
>Rhangqa imibala kuphindo olunzulu</guilabel
> ithetha ukuba noba okubhaliweyo okuphindiweyo ngapha kwamaxesha amathathu kuzakuvela kumbala.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="appearance-tab-layout">
<title
>Yaneke</title>

<para
><guilabel
>Bonisa uluhlu lwencwadi ende</guilabel
> ikuvumela uqhoboshe uluhlu lwencwadi olude ukuqala nokucima. Uluhlu lwencwadi olude lubonisa iincwadi zonke indlela ezantsi kwicala lasekhohlo lwe &kmail; iwindow engundoqo, ekuvumela ukuba ubone iincwadi ezininzi kunakwimboniselo emfutshane, kodwa ithatha kude esinye isithuba sokubonisela okubhaliweyo kwemiyalezo. Nge <guilabel
>Bonisa ubungakanani bomyalezo</guilabel
> ikhethiwe apho kuzakuba ngomnye umhlathi kulwahlulo lwe Header olubonisa ubungakanani bemiyalezo kwi bytes. <guilabel
>Uluhlu lomsonto womyalezo we header</guilabel
> izakubeka yonke imiyalezo kudidi lomthi, ngoko iimpendulo kumyalezo zisezantsi kwalo myalezo.</para>

<para
>Nge <guilabel
>iinketho zomsonto ze header yomyalezo</guilabel
> ungakhetha phantsi kweziphi iimeko imisonto ingavela ivulwe kokungagqibekanga (&ie; ayiwanga phantsi). Ungavula/vala imisonto usebenzisa i <guilabel
>+</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>-</guilabel
> amaqhosha ukuba awukhubazi oko apha.</para>

<para
>Nge <guilabel
>Uboniso loMhla</guilabel
> ungakhetha phakathi kwefomati ezininzi zomhla. I <guilabel
>Ifomati Yobulali</guilabel
> yile ungayikhankanya kwi &kcontrol;.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="appearance-tab-profiles">
<title
>Iimboniso zabucala</title>

<para
>Eli candelo likunika izicwangciso zokungagqibekanga ezininzi.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="appearance-tab-addressbook">
<title
>Incwadi yedilesi</title>

<para
>Eli candelo likuvumela ukhethe phakathi kweencwadi zedilesi ezininzi, njengoko i <guilabel
>Eyakwantu i KMail</guilabel
> ilula kakhulu ne <guilabel
>&kaddressbook;</guilabel
> iyephambili - siyaleza ukusebenzisa i &kaddressbook;. Qaphela ukuba ufuna upakisho lwe kdeutils ukusebenzisa i <guilabel
>KAB</guilabel
>.</para>

<para
>Ngexesha i <guilabel
>Eyakwantu i KMail</guilabel
> isiseko sedata sizimele (&ie; awuzukuzibona iidilesi kwi <guilabel
>KAB</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>&kaddressbook;</guilabel
> ukuba ungenise kuphela zona kwi <guilabel
>Eyakwantu i KMail</guilabel
> incwadi yedilesi), <guilabel
>KAB</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>&kaddressbook;</guilabel
> sebenzisa isiseko sedata esinye.</para>

</sect2>

