<sect1 id="composer-tab">
<title
>Isithuba soMqambi</title>

<sect2 id="composer-tab-general">
<title
>Ngokubanzi</title>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Amabinzana</guilabel
> icandelo likuvumela uchaze iilayini ezijikeleziswa ngokuzenzekelayo ezidityaniswe kwimpendulo yomyalezo, imiyalezo esiwe phambili, nokubhaliweyo okuphindiweyo. Kukho ezithile &percnt;-denoted abasebenzi abazakufaka amaxabiso athile. Ezi ziboniswa ngentla kwi <guilabel
>Amabinzana</guilabel
> icandelo: <symbol
>%D</symbol
> ukufaka umhla, <symbol
>%S</symbol
> ukufaka umxholo, <symbol
>%F</symbol
> ukufaka umthumeli, <symbol
>%%</symbol
> ukufaka uphawu lepesenti <symbol
>%_</symbol
> ukufaka isithuba, ne <symbol
>%L</symbol
> ukufaka ulwaphulo lwelayini. Ungadibanisa amabinzana empendulo kwiilwimi ezingaphandle kokungagqibekanga kwakho &kde; ulwimi usebenzisa i <guilabel
>Ulwimi</guilabel
> iqhosha. Oku kuzakusebenza kuphela kwiilwimi ezine i18n package oyifakileyo.</para>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Amathanda</guilabel
> umhlaba uqulathe umsebenzi ozakwenza uphindo lokubhaliweyo (uzakufuna ukusebenzisa okungagqibekanga).</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Fakela utyikityo ngokuzenzekelayo</guilabel
> ikuvumela uqhoboshe noba kukuquka ngokuzenzekelayo utyikityo lwakho njgoko kuchazwe kwi <link linkend="setting-your-identity"
>identity tab</link
>.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Sebenzisa uphindo olubukekayo</guilabel
> izakwaphula iilayini ezinde kodwa izakuzama ukugcina uphindo olululo (&eg; i <quote
>&gt; </quote
> izakusoloko ikwisiqalo selayini).</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Tyikitya ngokuzenzekelayo imiyalezo usebenzisa i PGP</guilabel
> ikuvumela uqhoboshe noba utyikitye ngokuzenzekelayo imiyalezo yakho ngokungagqibekanga. Kunjalo ungangakhethi i icon kwi window yomqambi yomyalezo ngamnye ukuba kuyimfuneko.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Usongo lwegama kumhlathi</guilabel
> ikuvumela ujike usongo lwegama ukuqala nokucima kwi <guilabel
>Iwindow yoMqambi</guilabel
> kwaye ikuvumela ucwangcise umhlathi apho amagama azakusongwa khona (awufuni noko ukutshintsha ixabiso elingagqibekanga, eliyi <userinput
>78</userinput
>).</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="composer-tab-editor">
<title
>Umhleli</title>

<para
>Ukuba awuyithandi i <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> ungasebenzisa umhleli owahlukileyo. Qaphela ukuba i <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window izakuvula kwaye umhleli wangaphandle uzakuvula ngoko ukuba uchwetheza nje umsebenzi omnye kumzimba womyalezo. Ukuba wenziwe, gcina okubhaliweyo kwaye khupha umhleli. Okubhaliweyo kuzakuvela ngoku kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window, apho ungayithumela khona.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="composer-tab-subject">
<title
>Umxholo</title>

<para
>Eli candelo liqulathe uluhlu lwezimaphambili ze <quote
>Phendula</quote
> ne <quote
>Phambili</quote
>. Ukuba wamkela imiyalezo esebenzisa izimaphambili ezahlukileyo kwezisezantsi, ungadibanisa apha ukuze &kmail; iziqonde (le ndlela &kmail; ingazilahla ukulungisa imiyalezo kwaye izibuyisele ngokukodwa).</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="composer-tab-charset">
<title
>Charset</title>

<para
>Kwi <guilabel
>Ezikhoyo i charsets</guilabel
> icandelo ongenza kulo i charsets ezikhoyo zemiyalezo yakho. I charsets kolu luhlu zivela kwezomqambi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Iinketho</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Cwangcisa i Enkhowudingi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> menu.</para>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Engagqibekanga i charset</guilabel
> icandelo likuvumela ukhethe engagqibekanga icharset yemiyalezo yakho. Ukuba ukhetha i <guilabel
>Sebenzisa eyakho engagqibekanga icharset xa uphendula okanye usisa phambili i</guilabel
>, icharset yomyalezo yoqobo izakulahlwa kwaye icharset yakho izakusetyenziswa ukuphendula nokusa phambili.</para>

</sect2>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="mime-tab">
<title
>&MIME; Headers Tab</title>
<!-- fixme in kmail, too: "headers tab" -->

<para
>I <guilabel
>Yenza owakho umyalezo-Id headers</guilabel
> icandelo likuvumela uchaze indlela imiyalezo yakho yomhlaba weMyalezo-Id izakujikeleziswa. Umyalezo-Id kufuneka ubenesimamva sehlabathi-esinye.Kuxhomekeke kolwakho ucwangciso, oku kunokuba ngumzekekelo. Kufuneka uthumele umyalezo kwaye jonga kwi header zayo. Ukuba iqulathe i Umyalezo-Id ophela nge <quote
>inginginya yobulali</quote
> okanye nawuphi na omnye umtya ongamelwa ngokuba mnye ofuna ukuwukhetha <guilabel
>Yenza umyalezo wakho-Id headers</guilabel
> kwaye cwangcisa esinye isimamva.. Into engcono kukusebeznisa igama lethambeka ongumninilo.</para>

<para
>I <guilabel
>Chaza amaphetshana eheader yemime esiko</guilabel
> icandelo licwangcisa iiheader i &kmail; ezakuzisebenzisa kwimiyalezo ephumayo. Ungafaka yomibini imihlaba emitsha kwaye ubhale ngaphezulu esele ikhona. Lo msebenzi uluncedo kuphela kubasebenzisi abaphambili.</para>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="security-tab">
<title
>Isithuba sokhuseleko</title>

<sect2 id="security-tab-general">
<title
>Ngokubanzi</title>

<para
><guilabel
>Khetha HTML kokubhaliweyo okungenanto</guilabel
> kuzakubonisa i <acronym
>HTML</acronym
> imiyalezo ngeyazo i <acronym
>HTML</acronym
> ufomato nobeko. Sazisa ngamandla ukushiya olu khetho lucimile, njengeengxaki zokhuseleko nge <acronym
>HTML</acronym
> inoku za. Xa olu khetho lucimile, ungafunda kwakhona <acronym
>HTML</acronym
> imiyalezo, kodwa njengokubhaliweyo okungenanto kuphela.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Layisha iintelekiso zangaphandle kumnatha</guilabel
> izakulayisha imifanekiso yangaphandle, amakhasi ohlobo &etc; kwi the internet xa ujonga kwi <acronym
>HTML</acronym
> umyalezo. Siyaleza ngamandla uku shiya olu khetho lucimile (noxa lungenasiphumo ukuba <guilabel
>Khetha HTML kokubhaliweyo okungenato</guilabel
> sele icimile). Ngokudibanisa ezangaphandle iintelekiso kwiposi zazo, abantu abathumela ispam bangabhaqa ukuba ujonge kumyalezo wabo. Qaphela ukuba olu khetho alunasiphumo kwi Java, Javascript ne Plagi - ezi zikhutyaziwe kwaye azina kwenziwa nakanye.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Thumela ngokuzenzekelayo iziqinisekiso zokwamkela nokufunda</guilabel
> izakuthumela ngokuzenzekelayo uqiniiseki (kwindlela yomyalezo omtsha) kumthumeli womyalezo ukuba  ucele oko. Ukuba ushiya olu khetho lucimile, akukho qinisekiso lizakuthunyelwa.Siyaleza ukushiya olu khetho lucimile. Ukuba ufuna ukuthumela iziqinisekiso kubantu abathile ungakwenza oko ngokusebenzisa i <guilabel
>qinisekisa uphathelo</guilabel
> intshukumo yecebo lokucoca.</para>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="security-tab-pgp">
<title
>PGP</title>

<para
>Ye <guilabel
>PGP</guilabel
> tab nceda bona i <link linkend="pgp-settings"
><application
>PGP</application
> icandelo</link
>.</para>

</sect2>

</sect1>

