<qandaset id="faq-set">

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Incwadi zam ziyakhula noba ndicima imiyalezo.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
> Ukususa ngenene imiyalezo ecinyiweyo kwi diski, kufuneka udibanise iincwadi zakho usebenzisa i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Dibanisa zonke iincwadi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> (ngokungagqibekanga, oku kuzakwenzeka lonke ixesha ukhupha i &kmail;).</para>
<para
>Ngoko ke, ngoku kukho ibug eyenze kukhupho lwe &kde; 2.2.0 (&kmail; 1.3): ngamanye amaxesha iincwadi azidityaniswa nakanye, noba ngencwadi okanye ngokuzenzekelayo. Nalu usebenzo jikelele: hlela i <filename
>~/.kde/share/config/kmailrc</filename
> ifayile, phendla zonke izenzeko ze <quote
>Ezimileyo=ubuxoki</quote
> kwaye zibuyisele nge <quote
>Emileyo=inyaniso</quote
> (&kmail; mayingasebenzi xa usenza oku). Le bug izakulungiswa kwi KDE 2.2.1 ezakukhutshwa ngenene ngo Septemba 2001. </para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>I <guilabel
>&lt;Ku okanye Cc&gt;</guilabel
> <guilabel
>ayi qulathanga</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
> icebo lokucoca alisebenzi.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Le asiyo bug, kodwa ayiqondi msinyane. Imvelaphi yokudideka ikhangeleka ikhondoza kwinyaniso ecingwa ngabantu <guilabel
>&lt;Ku okanye Cc&gt;</guilabel
> <guilabel
>ayiqulathanga</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
> inokuthetha ukuba noba <guilabel
>Ku</guilabel
> okanye <guilabel
>Cc</guilabel
> inokuqulatha <userinput
>xxx</userinput
>. Olu guqulelo licinga ukuba ukusebenzisa <guilabel
>ayiqulathanga</guilabel
> ithetha ukuyekwa komthetho wonke. Le asingomzekelo.</para>
<para
>Ngenene, <guilabel
>ayiqulathanga</guilabel
> yenye nje <emphasis
>umsebenzisi</emphasis
>, njenge <guilabel
>iqulathe</guilabel
>. Ayithe thi ukuba <quote
>yeka umthetho</quote
>. Nnjenge <guilabel
>&lt;Ku okanye Cc&gt;</guilabel
> <guilabel
>iqulathe</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
> ithetha ukuba <quote
><guilabel
>Ku</guilabel
> <guilabel
>iqulathe</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
> <emphasis
>okanye</emphasis
> <guilabel
>Cc</guilabel
> <guilabel
>iqulathe</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
></quote
>, <guilabel
>&lt;Ku okanye Cc&gt;</guilabel
> <guilabel
>ayiqulathanga</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
> ithetha ukuba <quote
><guilabel
>Ku</guilabel
> <guilabel
> ayiqulathanga</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
> <emphasis
>okanye</emphasis
> <guilabel
>Cc</guilabel
> <guilabel
>ayi qulathanga</guilabel
> <userinput
>xxx</userinput
></quote
>.</para>
<para
>Ungalinganisela okunye ukuziphatha ngokusebenzisa imithetho emibini: Omnye we <guilabel
>Ku</guilabel
> nomnye we <guilabel
>Cc</guilabel
>. Omnye wenguqulelo ezilandelayo ze &kmail; zizakuquka ujongo ngaphaya lophendlo, elizakuyenza yenzeke ukusebenzisa ngokulula imizekelo engasentla.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Xa ndiphendula kwi email kukho umsebenzi othile welayini enye phambi kotyikityo. Ndifumana isilumkiso malunga neqela lomsebenzi elitshintshiweyo xa ndizama ukuthumela iposi.</para
></question>
<answer>
<para
>Gqiba ku Qt-2.3.1.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingalufumana phi uluhlu lotshintsho phakathi kweenguqulelo ze &kmail;?</para
></question>
<answer>
<para
>Ikhusi lokwamkela lidwelisa lonke utshintsho olubalulekileyo lokhupho lwayo. Iboniswa xa uqala uguqulelo olutsha lwe &kmail; ixesha lokuqala. Ungasoloko ujonga kuyo kwakhona ngokukhetha isiqalelo sengcambu yoluhlu lwencwadi, &ie; <guilabel
>Iposi</guilabel
>.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingayiqwalasela indawo yolawulo lweposi yam?</para
></question>
<answer>
<para
>Khupha i &kmail;, yenza umva we <filename
>~/.kde/share/config/kmailrc</filename
>, ngoku yivule ngo mhleli kwaye dibanisa i &eg; <userinput
>folders=/home/username/.mail</userinput
> kwi <quote
>[General]</quote
> icandelo. Ngoku yisa zonke ezakho ezikhoyo iincwadi (uquka iifayile zesalathisi ezifihliweyo) kwindawo entsha. Ixesha elizayo uqala i &kmail; izakusebenzisa i <filename class="directory"
>/home/username/.mail</filename
> endaweni ye <filename class="directory"
>/home/username/Mail</filename
>. Qaphela ukuba i &kmail; izakulahla amacebo wayo ukuba utshintsha indawo yolawulo lweposi kodwa libala ukusa iincwadi zakho ezikhoyo.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Iqhosha lokutyikitya imiyalezo alenziwanga, lalenziwa kwixesha eladlulayo.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ngenisa eyakho i <guilabel
>PGP Uqwalaselo loMsebenzisi</guilabel
> kwi <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> incoko yababini yoqwalaselo. Ngaphandle kwe PGP Uqwalaselo loMsebenzisi &kmail; ayinakwazi ukuba sesiphi isitshixo esinokusetyenziswa ukutyikitya imiyalezo yakho ngayo.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingomnye wabo bantu abaneposi equlathe iilayini eziphindiweyo eziyi 100 ne layini enye ebhalwe ndim. Ngesinye isizathu (endingayifumaniyo) oku kucaphukisa abanye abantu. Inga &kmail; ndinceda kwaye yenze bonke ubomi bukabani bubengcono?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Kulungile. Khetha nje iqela elifutshane lweposi yoqobo nge mouse phambi kokuphendula.Leli qela kuphela elinokuphindwa kwimpendulo yakho. </para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>&kmail; iyalahleka/iyangqubana xa uthatha iposi.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Qiniseka ukuba unesithuba sediski esaneleyo. &kmail; ngoku ayiphathi imeko yediski epheleleyo ngenceba kwaye iyaphuma. Qaphela: &kmail; ikhusela idata yakho, imiyalezo engenakugcinwa kwi diski ishiywe kumncedisi.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ingaba i &kmail; incwadi yedilesi ixhasa uluhlu lonikezelo?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Hayi. Njengomsebenzi jikelele ungadibanisa ezininzi iidilesi ze email kungeno olunye lwedilesi ukuba usebenzisa i <quote
>eyakwantu</quote
> &kmail; incwadi yedilesi.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Kweminye imiyalezo ixabiso kwi <guilabel
>Umhla</guilabel
> umhlaba awulunganga, ubonisa i<guilabel
>Lwesithathu Dise 31 17:00:00 1969</guilabel
>.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ngenene i <quote
>Umhla:</quote
> header yale miyalezo yophukile, mhlawumbi ilahlekile kulwazi lommandla wexesha. Kulo mzekelo sidibanise usebenzo jikelele kwi mimelib. Kwi &kde; 2.2 mimelib liqela lopakisho lwe kdenetwork, kufuneka uqiniseke ukuba i &kde;'s mimelib iya setyenziswa kwaye hayi eyahlukileyo kwindlela yakho.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Utyikityo lwam lunezithuba ezimbini ngaphezu kwalo. Oku kundenza lusizi.</para
></question>
<answer>
<para
>Ukwahlula utyikityo kumzimba womyalezo ngodwi ababini ne sithuba yindlela eqhelekileyo neluncedo yodidi olusezantsi. Ukuba unokuva okunzima malunga nolu phakamiso uguqula kancinane i &kmail; imvelaphi ukususa laa layini.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

