<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>&kmail; ithatha imiyalezo eminye ngapha nangapha kwakhona.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Oku kuyenzeka ukuba une <guilabel
>Cima iposi ku mncedisi</guilabel
> engakhethwanga kwaye i POP3 umncedisi wakho akawuxhasi umyalelo we UIDL. Okwangoku akukho sebenzo jikelele ngaphandle kokukhetha i <guilabel
>Cima iposi kumncedisi</guilabel
>. Inkcazelo eneenkcukacha ezininzi ingafumaneka <ulink url="http://lists.kde.org/?l=kmail&amp;m=99220697415300&amp;w=2"
>kolu luhlu lokuposa leposi</ulink
>.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ingaba i &kmail; ixhsa i <acronym
>IMAP</acronym
>?</para
></question>
<answer>
<para
>Ewe, iyakwenza oko ukusukela &kde; uguqulelo 2.2. Asingomsebenzi ugqityiweyo noko, kodwa kuzakwanela kubasebenzisi abaninzi. Siyayazi loo misa, ngoko nceda sukuzingenisa iingxelo zoluhlu lomnqweno malunga nazo.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Kukho iibugs ezaziwayo kwi &kmail;?</para
></question>
<answer>
<para
>Ungalufumana uluhlu lwe bugs ezingenisiweyo kwi <ulink url="http://bugs.kde.org/db/pa/lkmail.html"
>bugs.kde.org</ulink
>. Qaphela ukuba ayisizizo zonke ezi bugs ezisebenzayo, ngoko ke sicinga ukuba i &kmail; liqhekeza elilungileyo lezixhobo ze computer.</para>
<para
><warning
><para
>Ngoko ke, awunakwenza &kmail; xa omnye umxhasi weposi sele enikezela iifayile kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
>. Ukuba uzama ukwenza oko, ungalahla imiyalezo. Qaphela ukuba ungenza izimamva zemiyalezo yakho nangayiphi na indlela.</para
></warning
></para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>&kmail; ayibonisi <acronym
>HTML</acronym
> posa njenge <acronym
>HTML</acronym
>, ndingabona kuphela imvelaphi.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Khetha <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Incwadi</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Khetha HTML kunokubhaliweyo okungenanto</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Kwizizathu zokhuseleko ungenza oko kuphela kwiposi ezithembakeleyo. Qaphela ukuba iiplagi (njenge <trademark class="registered"
>Macromedia</trademark
> <application
>Flash</application
>), Java ne Javascript ayizuku boniswa kwi &kmail; kwaye akukho ndlela yokuzisebenzisa.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingasebenzisa iinguqulelo ezahlukileyo ezimbini ze &kmail; ngexesha elinye? Ndingabuyela umva kuguqulelo langoku le &kmail; ukuya kwendala?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ungasebenzisa umzekelo omnye kuphela we &kmail; kanye. Siyaleza kwakhona ukuhlala kuguqulelo oluthile kwaye ungaswitshi emva naphambili phakathi kweenguqulelo ezahlukileyo. Ukuthoba kuguqulelo oludala kunokubangela iingxaki, &eg; kuba iifomati zefayile yesalathisi zinokutshintsha. Unyuso alunokubayingxaki.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ingaba i &kmail; ixhasa iifayile ezinga enkhowudwanga?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Hayi. Ngoko ke, ungaziphatha usebenzise icebo lokucoca, elichazwe kwi <ulink url="http://lists.kde.org/?l=kmail&amp;m=98908576320145&amp;w=2"
>thiyaposa</ulink
> kuluhlu lokuposa.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>&kmail; ingqubene xa bendibhala iposi. Ngoko le posi ilahlekile ngoku?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>&kmail; izama ukugcinaiposi yakho kwi <filename
>~/dead.letter</filename
> ukulalelisela ungqubano. Ixesha elizayo uqala i &kmail; umqambi weposi uzakuvela ngeposi yakho kwakhona. Ukuba ayenzeki, zama ukuvula <filename
>~/dead.letter</filename
> ngomhleli. Ukuba ayisekho, ungqubano lwaba lubi de i &kmail; ayakwazi ukugcina iposi yakho.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Xa ndizama ukucwangcisa incwadi ezakubaluluhlu lokuposa-lindela, ayenzi nantoni na xa isamkela i email kuluhlu.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ukwayamanisa incwadi ngoluhlu lokuposa akunanto yakwenza ngococo lwemiyalezo yoluhlu lokuposa. Uzakudibanisa umthetho omtsha wokucoca ngencwadi. Ngoko ke, xa wayamanise incwadi noluhlu lokuposa ungasebenzisa i <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Uluhlu Lempendulo...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> okanye <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Umyalezo omtsha...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> nedilesi yoluhlu lokuposa izakucwangciswa kwi <guilabel
>Ku:</guilabel
> umhlaba. </para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Umncedisi Wam we SMTP ufuna ububhali. Ingaba i &kmail; iyayixhasa?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Zimbini izixhobo ezisetyenziswayo eziqhelekilyo kububhali be SMTP: <quote
>SMTP emva POP3</quote
> ne <quote
>SMTP Auth</quote
>. <quote
>SMTP Auth</quote
> ayixhaswa ngoku. Ukusebenzisa <quote
>SMTP emva POP3</quote
> kufuneka uqokelele zonke iiposi zakho kwi <guilabel
>ibhokisi yaphandle</guilabel
> kwaye zithumele nje emva kokuba uthathe iposi entsha.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingasebenzisa i &kmail; ne <application
>procmail</application
>?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ewe, kodwa kubalulekile ukwenza yona ngendlela eyiyo okanye ungalahla iposi. Ukuze usebenzise iprocmail ne &kmail; ufuna ukucwangcisa i KMail ukuze ithathe iposi entsha kwiifayile ze spool apho iprocmail ilahla khona iposi yakho. Yenza <emphasis
>hayi</emphasis
> cwangcisa iprocmail ukusa iposi kwincwadi ye KMail, oku akunakusebenza.</para>
<para
>Kwifayile nganye ye spool ye procmail, ufuna ukwenza ityala apho i &kmail; izakuthatha khon aiposi. Ufuna kwakhona ukuqiniseka ukuba ukhankanya igama elililo lefayile yokutshixa yeli tyala. Xa ucwangcisa ityala, &kmail; izakwenza ulinganiso oluncinane kwifayile yakho ye procmail, kwaye izakuzama ukudwelisa ifayile ye spool nganye eyifumanayo, kwaye kwakhona neefayile zokutshixa ecaleni kwe "procmail lockfile" umba. iprocmail ivumela umsebenzi akhankanye iifayile zokutshixa ngendlela ezintathu ezahlukeneyo, ngoko akukho ndlela yokuseka uhambelwano phakathi kwefayile zespool nezokutshixa. Ngoko kuxhomekeke kuwe ngenene  ukuqinisekisa ukuba ukhankanya ifayile yokutshixa kwifayile nganye ye spool.</para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry id="pgp-faq">
<question
><para
>Kufuneka ndazi ntoni ukuba ndifuna ukusebenzisa <application
>PGP</application
>/<application
>GnuPG</application
> nge &kmail;?</para
></question>

<answer
><para
>&kmail; inikeza ujongano olucacileyo nolulula lwemisebenzi engundoqo wolu dweliso lweenkqubo. Kwakhona uzakuqonda indlela ezi nkqubo zisakusebenza ngayo nento ezakwenza usebenziso lwazo lukhuseleke.Imiba ethile ebalulekileyo:</para>

<itemizedlist
> <listitem
> <para
>U <emphasis
>ngenene</emphasis
> ungavavanya ukuba ufihlo luyasebenza phambi kokuba ulusebenzise. &kmail; ixhomekeke kwi <application
>PGP</application
>/<application
>GnuPG</application
>'s imitya yemposiso, etshintsha rhoqo phakathi kweenguqulelo ezahlukeneyo.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Ukuthemba isithsixo sikawonke-wonke sangaphandle ngaphandle kokusikhangela asiyongcamango ilungileyo.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>&kmail; ayizukufihla imiyalezo nge ngathembakelanga (engatyikitywanga) isitshixo sikawonke-wonke ukuba usebenzisa i <application
>PGP</application
>. Ukuba usebenzisa i <application
>GnuPG</application
> &kmail; <emphasis
>izaku</emphasis
> fihla imiyalezo ngezitshixo ezingathembakelanga zikawonke-wonke.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Njengabaninzi abaxhasi beposi, &kmail; ingafihla imiyalezo yakho, kodwa <emphasis
>hayi</emphasis
> izifakelo zakho. Kufuneka uzifihle ngencwadi phambi kokuba uzifakele.</para
> </listitem
> </itemizedlist>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndiza kuyicwangcisa njani i &kmail; ukusebenzisa i (&ie; funda kwaye ubhale) imiyalezo nge ngengabo-Latini1 abasebenzi?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Kwi <guilabel
>Inkangeleko</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>Imigca</guilabel
> icandelo le <guilabel
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guilabel
> incoko yababini, khetha elungileyo <guilabel
>Ucwanbbgciso loMsebenzi</guilabel
> woluhlu lomyalezo noluhlu lwencwadi. Ukuba <guilabel
>ikhowudi enye (iso10646-1)</guilabel
> ikhona, ungakhetha yona. Mhlawumbi imiyalezo ayikaboniswa kakuhle, ungasoloko uzama ezinye izicwangciso kwi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Umyalezo</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Cwangcisa Enkhowudingi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> menu. Yokubhala imiyalezo, yiya ku <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
>/<guilabel
>Charset</guilabel
> kwaye qwalasela engagqibekanga icharset ofuna ukuyisebenzisa kwezakho iiposi.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ukhangelo lopelo alubaqondi abasebenzi abangengo-mangesi.</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Phambi kokuba ungasebenzisa ukhangelo lopelo kwixesha lokuqala, ungayi qwalasela. Ungakwenza oko kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> window's menu phantsi <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Umkhangeli wopelo...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Ungacwangcisa idikshinari ne enkhowudingi apho.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndiyisebenzisa njani eyam i <application
>Eudora</application
>/&Netscape;/<application
>Ujongo</application
>/... iincwadi zeposi kwi &kmail;?</para
></question
> 
<answer
><para
>Bona icandelo <link linkend="importing"
>Usebenzisa ezinye iifayile zebhokisi yePosi Nge &kmail;</link
>.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingazisebenzisa njani iincwadi ezingekho kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail/</filename
>?</para
></question>

<answer
><para
>Yenza lula i symlink kweyakho i <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> ulawulo usebenzisa i <userinput
><command
>Kwi</command
> <option
>-s</option
> <filename
>/somewhere/Mail/mymailboxfile</filename
> <filename class="symlink"
>~/Mail/remote</filename
></userinput
>. Xa uqala i &kmail; uzakubona incwadi entsha ngegama i <guilabel
>bekela kude</guilabel
> equlathe iiposi kwincwadi yakho yobekelo kude. Ukuba ufuna ukudibanisa ulawulo lweposi lobekelo kude sebenzisa i <userinput
><command
>Kwi</command
> <option
>-s</option
> <filename
>/somewhere/Mail</filename
> <filename class="symlink"
>~/Mail/.remotedir.directory</filename
></userinput
>. Kulo mzekelo ufuna kwakhona ukwenza incwadi engenanto entsha ebizwa ngokuba yi <filename class="directory"
>remotedir</filename
> nge &kmail;. Incwadi eneenkcukacha <filename class="directory"
>remotedir</filename
> izakuqulatha ngoku zonke iincwadi zobekelo kude zebhokisi yeposi njengeencwadi ezisezantsi.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndingasebenzisa ufihlo ngeyam yesiqhelo (engeyo-<acronym
>SSL</acronym
>) <acronym
>POP3</acronym
> ityala?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ukuba owakho <acronym
>POP3</acronym
> umncedisi usebenzisa i <application
>ssh</application
> daemon, ungasebenzisa i ssh ukugquma eyakho i <acronym
>POP3</acronym
> udibaniso usebenzisa umyalelo olandelayo.</para>

<para
><userinput
><command
>ssh</command
> <option
>-L 110:127.0.0.1:110 user@host</option
></userinput
></para>

<para
>Guqula kancinane eyakho i &kmail; uqwalaselo ukuthatha iposi egqitha kwi <acronym
>POP3</acronym
> kwi <userinput
>inginginya yobulali</userinput
> ne ssh izakugquma udibaniso kuwe. Ufuna ukwenziwa ingcambu ukuphumeza lo myalelo. Ngokuhambelana, tshintsha inani lokuqala lezibuko, &ie; isenzeko sokuqala se <userinput
>110</userinput
>, kwinto engaphezulu 1024 kwaye qwalasela i &kmail; ukusebenzisa elo zibuko. <note
><para
>Ukuba ezinga-fihlwanga iiposi sele zithunyelwe ngokugqitha kwi internet, uncedo kuphela lokusebenaisa i <application
>ssh</application
> lelokuba eyakho i <emphasis
>igama eligqithisiweyo</emphasis
> lizakuthunyelwa ngokufihlakeleyo kwi <acronym
>POP3</acronym
> umncedisi.</para
></note
></para>
</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ingaba i &kmail; iyazitshixa iincwadi ezisebenzisayo?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>&kmail; ayizitshixi iifayile kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
>.</para>
<para
>Ukunqanda umngcipheko wokulahla iposi <emphasis
>ukuba usebenzisa elobulali ityala</emphasis
> kuyimfuneko ukuqinisekisa ukuba i &kmail; isebenzisa udidi olunye lokutshixa njengommeli wophathelo lweposi.</para>

<para
>Kukho iinketho ezintlanu ezahlukileyo zotshixo onokuzisebenzisa:</para>

<itemizedlist
> <listitem
><para
><guilabel
>Mutt dotlock (iyaleziwe)</guilabel
></para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><guilabel
>Mutt dotlock iphezulu</guilabel
></para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><guilabel
>Procmail ifayile yokutshixa</guilabel
></para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><guilabel
>FCNTL</guilabel
> (okungagqibekanga)</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><guilabel
>akukho nanye (sebenzisa ngononophelo)</guilabel
></para
></listitem
> </itemizedlist>

<para
><guilabel
>Mutt dotlock</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>Mutt dotlock iphezulu</guilabel
> zizakusebenzisa zombini icebo eliluncedo elincinane elivela nge mutt ebizwa ngokuba yi <command
>mutt_dotlock</command
>. <guilabel
>Mutt dotlock</guilabel
> ingasetyenziswa ngendlela enye njenge <guilabel
>Procmail ifayile yotshixo</guilabel
> ukhetho, ngomda omnye ngokhangelo kwi <filename class="directory"
>/var/spool/mail/</filename
> iincwadi. Ngoko ke, i <guilabel
>Mutt dotlock iphezulu</guilabel
> ukhetho lungenza iifayile zokutshixa kwi <filename class="directory"
>/var/spool/mail</filename
> ulawulo. <command
>mutt_dotlock</command
> ludweliso lwenkqubo yobeko lwegid kwaye olu khetho luzakuyisebenzisa kwindlela yobeko lwegid. Nceda qaphela ezi nketho zizakusebenza kuphela ukuba i mutt ifakiwe kwindlela yakho.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>Procmail ifayile yokuvala</guilabel
> izakusebenzisa icebo eliluncedo elincinane oluvela nge <application
>procmail</application
> ebizwa <command
>ifayile yokuvala</command
>. Ungasebenzisa oku ukuba incwadi yakho yeposi iku lawulo apho uneemvume zokubhala. Oku akuzukusebenza kweyakho i <filename class="directory"
>/var/spool/mail/user</filename
> ifayile kwemininzi imizekelo. Izakwenza i <filename
>.lock</filename
> iifayile kwelakho ityala xa i &kmail; ikhangela iposi entsha. Nceda qaphela ukuba oku kuzakusebenza kuphela ukuba <application
>procmail</application
> ifakwe kwindlela yakho.</para>

<para
><guilabel
>FCNTL</guilabel
>: ukhetho olungagqibekanga luzakusebenzisa i <function
>fcntl()</function
> ubizo lwendlela.</para>

<para
>Ukuba awufuni ukusebenzisa naluphi na utshixo, i <guilabel
>akukho nanye</guilabel
> ukhetho yilento uyifunayo. Ngoko ke, kukho imingcipheko yokulahla iposi xa kungekho lutshixo lusetyenziswayo.</para>

</answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndiyishiya njani iposi kumncedisi?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Vula i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guimenuitem
> </menuchoice
> window. Nqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umsebenzi womnatha</guilabel
> tab. Khetha ityala lakho kuluhlu lwetyala kwaye nqakraza i <guilabel
>Guqula kancinane...</guilabel
> iqhosha. Le ncoko yababini iqulathe i <guilabel
>Cima iposi ku mncedisi</guilabel
> isicwangciso omawungasikhethi.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndizifaka njani ngokuzenzekelayo ifooter zokubhaliweyo kwiiposi zam?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ifooter yokubhaliweyo ubizwa ngokuba yifayile yotyikityo. Khetha i <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
> <guimenuitem
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> Khangela kwi <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> tab ye <guilabel
>Khankanya utyikityo ngezantsi</guilabel
> umhlaba. Khetha iqhosha lonomathotholo kwaye uchwetheze utyikityo lwakho ngezantsi.</para
></answer
> 
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Kutheni i &kmail; indibuza ngendawo yefayile yam yotyikityo?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>&kmail; izakucela indawo yefayile yotyikityo lwakho ukuba ukhangele ukhetho <guilabel
>Yenza ngokuzenzekelayo utyikityo</guilabel
> kwi <guilabel
>Umqambi</guilabel
> tab ye <guilabel
>Qwalasela i &kmail;...</guilabel
> incoko yababini, kodwa awukhankanyanga fayile yotyikityo kwi <guilabel
>Uqwalaselo</guilabel
> tab. Uzakukhankanya noba ifayile yotyikityo, khetha i <guilabel
>Sebenzisa utyikityo ngezantsi</guilabel
>, okanye sukukhetha i <guilabel
>Yenza ngokuzenzekelayo utyikityo</guilabel
>.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Ndiyicwangcisa njani <application
>thumela iposi</application
> ukusebenza nge &kmail; ukuba ndinodibaniso locofo-phezulu?</para
></question
> 

<answer
><para
