>.</para
></answer>
</qandaentry>

<qandaentry>
<question
><para
>Sizibonile iinkcazelo zokuziphatha kolawulo lobekelo kude nge &kmail;. Ilapho naluphi na uxwebhu kujongano olukhoyo?</para
></question>
<answer
><para
>Ungafumana uluhlu lwemisebenzi ngokusebenzisa lo myalelo kwiqokobhe: <userinput
