<chapter id="importing">
<title
>Usebenzisa ezinye Iifayile zebhokisi yePosi nge &kmail;</title>

<para
>&kmail; inikeza isixhobo sorhwebo lwangaphakathi kwifomati ezithile. Unganikeza yona usebenzisa <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Ifayile</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Rhweba ngaphakathi...</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>. Ufuna kuphela esinsiqendu ukuba esi sixhobo asikusebenzeli.</para>

<para
>Eli candelo lwabo bonke abasebenzisi abafuna ukusa imiyalezo ye email kodlulileyo umxhasi we email ngapha kwi &kmail;. &kmail; igcina eyayo iposi usebenzisa i <literal
>mbox</literal
> fomati, enye yezibninzi ezisetyenziswayo iifomati zebhokisi yeposi kwi &UNIX; iindlela. Mbox iibhokisi zigcina imiyalezo kwifayile enye, iqwalasela apho imiyalezo iqala khona nalapho iphela khona nge i <literal
>Kwi</literal
> ilayini (sukuxuba oku nge <literal
>Kwi:</literal
> header equlathe umthumeli womyalezo). Kwezininzi &UNIX; udweliso lweenkqubo zeposi, konke omawukwenze kukusa ezakho iibhokisi zeposi kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> (okanye yenza i <filename class="symlink"
>Iposi</filename
> ikhonkco elinophawu kwincwadiequlathe iibhokisi zeposi zakho), qiniseka ukuba ziyabhaleka ngomsebenzisi wakho, kwaye yazisa i &kmail;. Iibhokisi zeposi zizakuza ngoku kakuhle kwi &kmail;.</para>

<para
>Ukuba ezindala iibhokisi zeposi azikho kwifomati ye mbox, bona ngezantsi imiyalelo ekurhwebeni ngaphakathi ezinye iifomati eziqhelekileyo. Thatha ujongo kwi <ulink url="http://kmail.kde.org/download.html"
>Icandelo lolayisho phantsi lwe &kmail;'s iphepha lasekhaya</ulink
> ukuba ifomati yebhokisi yeposi ayidweliswanga apha.</para>

<warning
><para
>Sukusebenzisa umxhasi wesibini weposi onikeza iifayile kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> ngexesha i &kmail; isebenza okanye ungalahla imiyalezo. Eli candelo licacisa kuphela indlela yokurhweba ngaphakathi iibhokisi zeposi kwi &kde; kanye, ayiloncedo kuwe ukuba uceba ukusebenzisa abaxhasi beposi abaninzi bebhokisi zakho zeposi kwixesha elizayo.</para
></warning>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><application
>Eudora Lite</application
>/<application
>Eudora Pro</application
></term
> <listitem
> <para
><application
>Eudora</application
> isebenzisa ifomati ye mbox kwiifayile zayo zeposi. Ukuzisebenzisa nge &kmail;, qiniseka ukuba eyakho i <application
>Eudora</application
> iibhokisi zeposi zilinganisiwe, ngoku khuphela i <literal role="extension"
>.mbx</literal
> iifayile (&Windows; <application
>Eudora</application
>) okanye <application
>Eudora</application
> iifayile zebhokisi yeposi (&Mac; <application
>Eudora</application
>) kweyakho <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> ulawulo. Awufuni kukhuphela <filename
>isalathisi</filename
> iifayile. Xa uqala i &kmail;, iibhokisi zeposi zinokuvela kulwahlulo lweencwadi nemiyalezo inokunikezwa kulwahlulo lwe Headers.</para
> <para
>Ukuba imiyalezo ayiveli kulwahlulo lwe Headers, iifayile zakho zebhokisi yeposi zinokuqulatha i &Windows; okanye &Mac; abasebenzi botyiso lwelayini. Sebenzisa owakho umhleli wokubhaliweyo omthandayo, i <application
>ikhowudi kwakhona</application
> umyalelo okanye ulwimi olushicilelayo ukutshintsha i &Windows; okanye &Mac; ilayini ityisa kwi &UNIX; ilayini ityisa.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>MMDF</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le fomati ikufutshane ngokwaneleyo kwifomati yebhokisi yeposi i &kmail; enokwazi ukusebenzisa ezi bhokisi zeposi ukuba ukhuphela nje zona kweyakho i <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> ulawulo. Ngoko ke, MMDF iibhokisi zeposi azivavanywanga nge &kmail;, ngoko iziphumo zakho zinokwahluka. Ukuba ungafumana le fomati ukusebenza nge &kmail;, nceda sazise ukuze siquke izalathisi ezininzi kukhupho loxwebhu olukhankanyiweyo olulandelayo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>MH iibhokisi zeposi</term
> <listitem
> <para
>MH iibhokisi zeposi zingabalawuli abaqulathe iifayile ezihambelana nomyalezo ngamnye kulo bhokisi yeposi. Iqokobhe lokushicilelweyo ukuguqula MH iibhokisi zeposi kwi mbox iibhokisi zeposi, <command
>mh2kmail</command
>, iyaqukwa noko kukhupho lwemvelaphi ye &kmail;, kodwa mhlawumbi kukhupho olupakishiweyo. Ukwenza olu shicilelo kwi MH incwadi kuzakuguqula yona kwi mbox fayile. Siphakamisa ngamandla ukuba ubuyisela eyakho i MH iincwadi zeposi phambi kokuba usebenzise olu shicilelo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Forte <application
>Ummeli</application
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Kwi <application
>Ummeli</application
>:</para
> <procedure
> <step
> <para
>Khetha imiyalezo ukurhweba ngaphandle</para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Khetha <menuchoice
><guimenu
>IFAYILE</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>GCINA IMIYALEZO NJENGE</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
></para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Phawula i <guilabel
>UNIX FORMAT</guilabel
> ne <guilabel
>GCINA KRWADA</guilabel
> iibhokisi</para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Nika ifayile i <literal role="extension"
>.txt</literal
> ulwandiso no gcino.</para
> </step
> </procedure
> <para
>Kwi &kde;:</para
> <procedure
> <step
> <para
>Okudlulileyo okusiweyo kugcina ifayile kwelungileyo i <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> incwadi eneenkcukacha</para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Nika kwakhona ifayile igama ngaphandle <literal role="extension"
>.txt</literal
> ulwandiso</para
> </step
> </procedure
> <para
>Xa uvula i &kmail; incwadi entsha ngemiyalezo eyiyo izakuba lapho.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>&Netscape; Iposi</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Khuphela eyakho &Netscape; iifayile zeposi kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/nsmail/</filename
> kwi <filename class="directory"
>~/Mail</filename
> kwaye qiniseka ukuba ziyabhaleka (kuphela ngomsebenzisi wakho, kunjalo). Iibhokisi zeposi zizakubakhona kwi &kmail; kwixesha elizayo uyiqala.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><application
>Iposi ye Pegasus</application
></term
> <listitem
> <para
><application
>Pegasus</application
> ye win32 isebenzisa iifayile ezizodwa zencwadi ezineenkcukacha zePosi ezifana kwi &kmail;. <application
>Pegasus iposi</application
> iifayile zencwadizinolwandiso <literal role="extension"
>.pmm</literal
> kodwa ziyifomati enye ne mbox ngaphandle kokuba imiyalezo ayiqali nge <literal
>Kwi</literal
> header, kodwa ngomsebenzi wolawulo. Ukusebenza jikelele kule, buyisela umzekelo ngamnye womsebenzi wolawulo nge <literal
>Kwi aaa@aaa Mvulo Jan 01 00:00:00 1997</literal
>. Le <literal
>Kwi</literal
> layini izakubayilayini yokuqala yomyalezo ngamnye, phambi kwe <literal
>Yamkelwe:</literal
> nezinye iiheader. Qiniseka ukusebenzisa umhleli wokubhaliweyo okuvumela ukuba ugcine iifayile kwi &UNIX; fomati okanye yenza iincwadi ezintsha kwi <application
>Pegasus</application
> akwi &UNIX; fomati kwaye khuphela iiposi zakho apho.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Maildir / Outlook Express / xfmail</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Izixhobo ukuguqula ezi fomati zikhoyo kwi <ulink url="http://kmail.kde.org/download.html"
>icandelo loLayisho phantsi le &kmail;'s iphepha lasekhaya</ulink
>.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Lotus <application
>Iziqwalaselo</application
>, BeOS Iifayile zePosi, <application
>cc: Mail</application
>, &etc;...</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Kuqala kufuneka ujonge kwi <ulink url="http://kmail.kde.org/download.html"
>Icandelo lolayisho phantsi lwe &kmail;'s iphepha lasekhaya</ulink
> ukuba kuukho izixhobo ukuguqula iiposi.</para
> <para
>Udweliso lweenkqubo zeposi azidweliswanga apha okanye kwiphepha lasekhaya azisebenzi nge &kmail; njengoko zisebenzisa iifomati zeposi apho i &kmail; ingenakuqonda. Ngoko ke, akukho ngozi ekuzameni! Ukuba ifayile yebhokisi yeposi ijongeka ngokufanayo kwifomati yebhokisi yeposi, zama ukumelana nefayile yebhokisi yeposi (khumbula, ifayile yesalkathisi ayifuneki) kweyakho i <filename
>~/Mail</filename
> ulawulo kwaye bona okwenzekayo ukuba uqala i &kmail;. Ukuba ufumana iibhokisi zeposi kumxhasi weposi omthandayo ukusebenza kwi &kmail;, nceda sixelele indlela oyenze ngayo ukuze ziquke izalathisi kuphindo lwexesha elizayo lolu xwebhu. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>
