<sect1 id="getting-kmail">
<title
>Ungayifumana njani i &kmail;</title>

<para
>&kmail; yinxenye ye &kde; projekti <ulink url="http://www.kde.org"
>http://www.kde.org</ulink
>. &kmail; ingafunyanwa kupakisho lwe kdenetwork kwi <ulink url="ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/"
>ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/</ulink
>, engundoqo &FTP; inxuwa le &kde; projekti. </para>
</sect1>

<sect1 id="compilation">
<title
>Uqokelelo no Fako</title>

<para
>Ukuze uqokelele kwaye ufake i &kmail; kwindlela yakho, chwetheza okulandelayo kulawulo lesiseko lonikezelo lwe kdenetwork:</para>

<screen width="40">
<prompt
>%</prompt
> <userinput
><command
>./configure</command
></userinput>
<prompt
>%</prompt
> <userinput
><command
>yenza</command
></userinput>
<prompt
>%</prompt
> <userinput
><command
>yenza</command
> <option
>faka</option
></userinput>
</screen>

<para
>Ukusukela ukuba i &kmail; isebenzisa i <application
>qwalasela ngokuzenzekelayo</application
> ne <application
>yenza ngokuzenzekelayo</application
> unokuba nengxaki yokuyiqokelela. Xa uneengxaki nceda zixele kwi &kde; uluhlu lokuposa.</para>

</sect1>

